Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盯住他！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Pick him up! Pick him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！ 我的意思是，法官大人 射得好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Son of a bitch! l mean, your Honour, that was a hell of a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我实习当见习律师 拿取额外的两个学分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm currently doing an ''externship'' for two extra credits as a clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是何锡栋法官 - B.J.何锡栋？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Judge Hookstratten. - B.J. Hookstratten?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那比名列首百分之五的高材生 更加出众\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's more impressive than being in the top five percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 华尔街有什么职位给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't know what kind of offers you've had from Wall Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.34,0:01:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是班里的头五名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The top five, sir. ln my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是头百分之五 对不起，我只想...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Not the top five percent. l'm sorry, l just...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦先生，我们给你 年薪六万八千元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. McDeere. We've just offered you $68,000 a year -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芝加哥著名的律师行的职位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- from arguably the leading law firm in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还要到别处吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ls there somewhere else you have to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是我工作的午膳时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm on lunch break from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你有很多选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know you've had a lot of offers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有一百二十七个客户 是“财富五百” 里的公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We have 1 27 clients that are Fortune 500 companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们愿意给你七万四千元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We'll offer you $7 4,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首年初级律师只需要二千小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...for a 1st-year associate is only 2,000 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是一般的二千七百小时 我门想你公余时自在一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Not the usual 2,700. We want you to have a life outside the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是湖人队球迷 我们在大球场有个厢座\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf you're a Lakers fan, we have a box at the Forum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道全国很多公司 都想以高薪招揽你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know firms from all over the country are offering you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以你的野心，只有一处适合你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}With your ambition, there's only one place for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我们的公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And that's with our firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先谈一下我们的实力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Let's start talking about what's in the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的合伙人包括一个前州长 两个众议员...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Our partners include an ex-Governor, two Congressmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个前农业部长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}a former Secretary of Agriculture...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生，要放下你的大衣吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}May l check your coat, sir?.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦先生，是吧？我是靳力万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. McDeere, right? l'm Marc Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介绍你认识林利华 他是我们的高级合伙人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'd like you to meet Oliver Lambert. He's our senior partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好 - 这位是马洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- How do you do, sir?. - This is Royce McNight -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们的行政合伙人 - 你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- our managing partner. - How do you do, sir?.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要喝点东西吗？ - 不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Care for a drink?. - No, l'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊，坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Take a seat, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 厌倦了面试吧？ - 不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}-Tired of interviews? - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 只是不知道该说什么 - 对律师来说是罕见的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Just don't quite know what to say. - Unusual for a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多情况会令我结舌的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can get tongue-tied in any number of situations, sir -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但经常都跟我太太有关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- but it's usually with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可介意形容其中一个 跟你太太的情况？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Would you mind describing one? With your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看见她 我们吵架时...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The first time l saw her... Any time we argue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.86,0:03:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她走进房间里...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Whenever she walks into a room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你其他的家人呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And the rest of your family?.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲在煤矿遇难去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}My father was killed in the coal mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母亲再嫁后住在佛罗里达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}My mother remarried and lives in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 兄弟姐妹？ - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Brothers and sisters? - None.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊，希望你不会 认为我们唐突，但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mitch, l hope you don't think us intrusive, but -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家庭安定对于我们特别重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- stability in the family has a special importance for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彭林骆只是孟菲斯市的 一间公司，有四十一位律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Bendini, Lambert & Locke is just a small Memphis firm, 41 lawyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们是个大家庭 所以我们很小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But we're a large family. So, we're careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在，先生...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Now, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么想问吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Do you have any questions for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们心目中可有安排？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Do you have an offer in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它包括分红制、低息按揭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt includes a bonus schedule, a low-interest mortgage -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你可以买一间屋 乡村俱乐部会籍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}so you can buy a home,country club membership,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们租借一辆新的平治给你 - 颜色由你来挑选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- We'll lease you a new Mercedes. - You pick the colour, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力万！你没有留心 颜色由他太太选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Lamar, you haven't been paying attention . His wife picks the color.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我在这里拆开它？ - 当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Do l open it here? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你知道里面有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Unless you can tell us what's in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那样薪酬条件的律师 也不用打开那个信封了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}A lawyer worth that offer shouldn't have to open the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:05:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马先生，你是公司的 行政合伙人，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. McKnight, you are the managing partner of the firm, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林先生对于我的聘用 可曾给你指示？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Did Mr. Lambert give you instructions regarding my employment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马先生，你一向都依照 林先生的指示做吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. McKnight, do you usually follow Mr. Lambert's instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反对、含糊、不明确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Objection. Vague, ambiguous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反对有效\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些指示究竟是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What precisely were those instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是炙手可热的 我要在形成争相竞夺之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You were in demand and l should make certain to obtain your services -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保证得到你的加盟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- before a bidding situation developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎样得到保证呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How did you go about making certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我贿赂了一个哈佛的文员 得到你最高薪酬条件的数目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l bribed a clerk at Harvard for the exact amount of your highest offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，增加了20%\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}and then added 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们公司给你的那封信 是我们唯一发出的一封\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mitch, the letter you got from our firm was the only one sent out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对你志在必得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在要走了 我丈夫很快就回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK. You have to leave now. l'm expecting my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The hell with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木须肉、四川牛肉、烧鸭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Moo Shoo Pork, Szechuan Beef, Mandarin Duck...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小王店的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...from Wong Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还有美酒 - 什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's even got a cork. - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得那间在孟菲斯的律师行 给我的信吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You remember the letter l got from that firm in Memphis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 孟菲斯？ - 我也那么想，直至提出条件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Memphis? - That's what l thought. Till their offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有什么条件？ - 他们没有说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What was the offer?. - They didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还封着的 - 我靠猜测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's sealed. - l guessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？ - 我猜测很了得的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What? - Yeah, l'm a good guesser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二年还会加薪百分之五\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Plus a five percent increase the second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么？ - 为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Why?. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是帮哪一方的？ - 你的一方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Whose side are you on? - Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有分红，低息按揭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Plus bonuses, plus a low-interest mortgage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 周围有草地的屋？ - 他们要我们去孟菲斯看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- As in home with grass around it? - They want to fly us to Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豪华轿车也不外如是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Been in one limo, you been in them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hey, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先会见初级律师行，然后在 私人宴会厅跟合伙人吃午饭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Associates first, then lunch with the partners in our private dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们的头号招聘对象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's our number one draft pick and -
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且纽约和芝加哥的大行 也向他招手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- he's being romanced by the big boys from New York and Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们要向他推销 我们这间孟菲斯的小公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So, we have to sell him on our little firm here in Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时…他要设法避免尴尬了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Meanwhile, he's gonna try not to be embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:09:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想提醒你们，他即将在哈佛 以荣誉成绩毕业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- while l remind you that he's about to graduate from Harvard with honours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 公司里没有人离了婚？ - 公司里没有人离了婚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- No one's divorced in the firm? - No one's divorced in the firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不可能的 - 也没有王老五\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lmpossible. - No bachelors either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 女人呢？ - 曾经有一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What about women? - They had one once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 只有一个？ - 穿着四英寸高跟鞋的高爱丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Only one? - Alice Krauss hobbled on 4'' heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害的踏高跷行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Affirmative Action on stilts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是白种已婚男人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}All white, all male, all married, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这到底是什么？ - 他来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What the hell is this? - There he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的步伐跟北部不同 我们是比较庄重的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The pace is different from the North. We're stately by comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殷勤但不好管闲事 我们互相保守秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Courteous and not as gossipy. We keep each other's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我喜欢那样 - 你喜欢它什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l like that. - What do you like about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的，这是个大家庭 像你说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}All of it. lt's a family. Just the way you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在波士顿的一间私立学校 教了数年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}For the last few years l've been teaching in Boston at a private school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有工作吗？ - 力万进了法学院后就没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Do you work?. - Not since Lamar was in law school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 工作不会被禁的 - 被禁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Working isn't forbidden. - Forbidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 工作...公司的主意 - 它怎可以被禁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Working... by the firm. - How could it be forbidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，我在十四个月内 生了两个孩子，又有很多家务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt isn't. Two babies in 1 4 months and l had all the work l could handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有计划生孩子吗？ - 可能在两、三年后吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Do you plan to start a family?. - Maybe in a couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 公司鼓励生育的 - 他们怎么做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- The firm encourages children. - How do they do that exactly?.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎样？ - 怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Hey, how about it! - How about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，那 “爱之船”乐队 那秘制排骨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK, OK. The Love Boat band, the secret recipe ribs -
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它们也许有点老套 - 我不介意老套，我喜欢老套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- they're a little square maybe. - l don't mind square. l like square.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- “古怪” 我就介意 - 什么意思， “古怪” ？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- 'Weird'' l mind. - What do you mean 'weird''?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个说法： 公司不 “禁止” 我去找工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Here's a quote： The firm does not forbid me to take a job -
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也鼓励生育，怎会那样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}and they encourage children. Ask me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 因为他们喜爱孩子 - 因为孩子带来安定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Because they love kids. - Because children promote stability.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 想听多一些吗？ - 不用，你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Want to hear more? - No, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管它的，我从栏杆跳下去好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Don't pay any attention. l'm just gonna throw myself over the rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的意向是无须解释的 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- My will is self-explanatory. - OK, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩，这些都是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}These are nice people, Abby. These are nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比你的看法好一点 你适应一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK, l'm more impressed with it than you are. You grew up with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可知道在这里 年薪九万六千元是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Do you know what $96,000 a year is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是在纽约的十五万，你可曾 想过我会有六位数字的薪金？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's a 150 in New York. Did you ever think l'd make a six-figure salary?.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 当然有 - 你有？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Absolutely. - You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你的家人 只是离这里几小时路程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Your folks are only a few hours away too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是说如果我们吵架 我也不用架长途车程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You mean if we fight, l don't have far to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她从酒店打出两个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}She made two phonecalls from the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个给她的父母 一个给孟菲斯学校委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}One to her parents and one to the Memphis School Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像有点勉强 我不想失去这个年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}She seemed a little reluctant. l'd hate to lose this young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我相信她会让步的 - 郭文迪和何约瑟又怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l think she'll come around. - What about Kozinski and Hodges?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你跟芝加哥的人谈过没有？ - 谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Have you spoken to Chicago? - l have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙，我们要想个办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's not good. We're gonna have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些开心的面孔是我画的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l drew the happy faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟菲斯在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Where's Memphis?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就是这间？ - 看来不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- ls that it? - lt looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比他们寄来的照片还更漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's prettier than the pictures they sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“文俊和艾佩 我们给你们暂时布置一下”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''Mitch and Abby, we've furnished the house for you temporarily.''
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“只是想你们感觉在家一样 希望你们不会介意”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''Just a few things to make you feel at home. Hope you don't mind.''
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Abby?.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不错吧？ - 你的呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Not bad, huh? - Where's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别起来 - 放心吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Don't get up. - Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦文俊 - 迫不及待上班吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Mitchell McDeere. - A tad eager, are we, Mr. McDeere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（郭文迪）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛？ 杜志说你六点半就来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What are you doing? Dutch says you've been here since 6：30.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要全力应付执业考试 - 好，从没有初级律师不合格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Thought l'd jump start the bar exam. - Good. No associate ever fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我带你去你的新办公室 - 赫华里...合约科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'll show you your new office. - Wally Hudson, Contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这有助你考执业试 公司从没有人不合格的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Here to help with the bar exam. No one at the firm has ever failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一天是四小时的 道德规范选择题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The first day's a 4-hour multiple choice on ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先看最初的六课 星期三八点四十五分见吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Look at the first 6 chapters. l'll see you Wednesday, 8：45.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这间公司从没有初级律师 考执业试不合格的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No associate of this firm has ever failed the bar exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:16:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 高肯尼...内部关系科 - 候米奇...遗嘱及遗产科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Ken Curry, Domestic Relations. - Mike Hill, Wills and Estates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，他妈的！ 不要...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Nina, fuck! Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对不起，我可以帮你吗？ - 其实是我来帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'm sorry. Can l help you? - Actually, l think l'm here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是杜韦利，你的指定导师 我们去吃午饭吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm Avery Tolar, your designated mentor. Let's go to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 午饭？现在还没有... - 还没有到中午，我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Lunch? But it's not even-- - Not even noon. l know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是工作午餐，来我的办公室 我先放下这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt'll be a working lunch. Come on up to my office while l drop this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,营业额就是一切 即使你在想着客户的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Billing is everything. The hours you spend even thinking about a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你是在交通挤塞时 还是在剃须或是坐在公园长椅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't care if you're stuck in traffic or shaving or sitting on a park bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我的专长是... - 替离岸机构设立有限公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Now, my particular field-- - is forming limited partnerships -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要是在开曼群岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- for offshore corporations, mainly in the Cayman lslands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我想你翻阅我上次 替客户葛善礼做的一宗案例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Good. l want you to review the last one l did for our client Sonny Capps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年赚了一千四百万 付了百分之四的说他十分愤恨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Made $1 4 million last year, paid 4%/ in taxes and resents every buck, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他给了我们四十万律师费 所以别令他不快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...he paid us $400,000 in fees, so don't make him unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看一下那宗交易 看你能否找到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Look at the deal. See if you can find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 美芝，说我迟一点找他 - 我该留着这些吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Madge, tell him l'll call later. - Shall l save these for later?.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麻烦你 - 你说“找到什么” 有何意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Could you please? - What do you mean by ''anything''?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你认为我有何意思？ - 我不知道，你才是风险专家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What do you think l mean? - l don't know. You're the risk taker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你以为我是指犯法？ - 不，是你想 “扭曲” 它多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You think l mean breaking the law?. - No, how far you want it ''bent''.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 尽力而为，只要不把它折断 - 即是说不要冒税局核数的险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- As far as you can without breaking it. - ln other words, don't risk an audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管核数 他们最好不要赢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't give a damn about an audit. They just better not win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 戴先生 - 午饭前先喝点东西吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Yes, Mr. Tolar. - Something before lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该警告你 公司不喜欢在办公时间喝酒的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l should warn you. The firm frowns on drinking during office hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麻烦你冻茶 - 孟买马丁尼加冰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lce tea, please. - Bombay martini on the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以来一些轻微的造反\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm allowed a few minor rebellions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麻烦你放在浴室里 - 亲爱的，我泡了茶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Put that in the bedroom, please. - Hey, hon, l made some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你，我从来没试过 这么多人替我做事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Please, l've never had so many people trying to do things for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩，这是南部 我们是用殷勤款待来烦你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's the South, Abby. We encumber you with hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想电话安装快速拨号吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Do you want your phone programmed for speed dialing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我丈夫的办公室号码 让我看...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Other than my husband's office number, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有的，麦太太...律师行的 安装工作都是我们做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We have it, Mrs. McDeere. We do all the installations for the Firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么引发你去念法律？ - 记不起了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What led you to law school? - l can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得的，顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sure you can, Counsellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在一间薄饼店当送货员 一天店主收到税单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l was a delivery boy for a pizza parlour. The owner got a notice from the lRS.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个移民 对英语或者所得税都一窍不通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He was an immigrant, didn't know English or about withholding tax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他破了产，失去他的店铺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He went bankrupt. Lost his store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我第一次想过要当律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That was the first time l thought of being a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是说，你是个理想主义者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ln other words, you're an idealist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,税务律师不是理想主义者 他失掉店铺时，我也失掉工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Tax lawyers are not idealists. When he lost his store, l lost my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它吓怕了我 - 因为失业？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt scared me. - Being out of work?.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 政府可以 “干掉” 任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No, the government can ''do'' anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么引发你念法律？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What led you to law school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是很久以前的事 我记不起了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's so far back l don't think l can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得的，顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sure you can, Counsellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前替年轻律师 和他们的妻子当球童\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l used to caddy for young lawyers and their wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到那些修长棕色的腿 就知道我要做律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l looked at those long tan legs and just knew l had to be a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些妻子也有修长棕色的腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The wives had long tan legs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.69,0:20:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿李，再来一杯马丁尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Ellis, another martini, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那么我们都不是理想主义者 - 但愿不是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- So, we're not a couple of idealists. - Heaven forbid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去告诉靳太太你们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll let Mrs. Quinn know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你肯定是今天吗？ - 他是那样告诉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Are you sure it's today?. - That's what he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 琪？ - 发生了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Kay?. - There's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郭文迪和何约瑟死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Marty Kozinski and Joe Hodges were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们大约二十分钟前听到的 你们在烧烤聚会时见过他们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We just heard about 20 minutes ago. Did you meet them at the barbecue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 发生了什么事？ - 我们不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What happened? - We're not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:21:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在开曼的一艘船上 准备潜水时发生爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They were diving off a boat on Grand Cayman when there was an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力万？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Lamar?.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文迪是...他的双胞胎女儿 比我们的儿子大一个月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Marty was-- His twin girls are a month older than our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很难过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm very sorry, Lamar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事，利华想我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}By the way, Oliver wanted me to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用担心学生贷款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...you shouldn't be burdened with a student loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天把文件带回去 公司会代你还款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Bring the papers by tomorrow. The firm will repay it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 琪很害怕 - 什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Kay was scared. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她是难过 - 难过和害怕是不同的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- She was upset. - ''Upset'' and ''scared'' are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她是害怕 - 怕什么？你那么了解她吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- She was scared. - Of what? Do you know her that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许不是 但最近我经常跟她在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Maybe not. But l've spent a lot of time with her lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们拥有两匹马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They have their own horses. Two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四分一里夸特马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Quarterhorses.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加起来就是半匹马？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Does that make half a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻抹去我们眼中的泪水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And gently wipe away every tear from our eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:23:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因圣父、圣子和圣灵之名 阿们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ln the name of the Father, and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们祷告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主啊，你时常诚心而快捷地 施予怜悯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Lord, our God, you are always faithful and quick to show mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的弟兄文迪 突然而剧烈地离开我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Our brother Marty was suddenly and violently taken from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你快帮助他，怜悯他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Come swiftly to his aid. Have mercy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并借着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And comfort his family and friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十字架的力量和保护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}by the power and protection of the cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们向上主祈求，阿们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We ask this through Christ our Lord. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在上主的安宁中离去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Let us go in the peace of Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟利华道别，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm just going to go say goodbye to Oliver. OK?.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会来找你 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'll catch up with you. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦太太？我是杜韦利 - 是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Mrs. McDeere? l'm Avery Tolar. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近这么少见我的丈夫 就是因为你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're the reason l see so little of my husband these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是世上最具野心的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He must be the most ambitious man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 其中一个吧 - 不，我是说每天舍得留下你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- One of them. - No, l mean... leaving you every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...just to go off to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定你应付得来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm sure you can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.84,0:24:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我怎样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Just tell me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.35,0:24:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你熟识他们吗？ 那两个去世的人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Did you know them well? The men who died?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.88,0:24:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熟识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很难过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You must be overwhelmed with grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦太太 人们有不同的方法哀悼的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}People grieve in different ways, Mrs. McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.55,0:25:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Abby?.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.09,0:25:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Come here a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.93,0:25:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“放弃了等候 跟带信人分享那碗狗粮吧”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''Gave up waiting. Share bowl of kibble with bearer of note.''
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.67,0:25:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.14,0:25:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他在里面？ - 是的，杜先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- ls he here? - Yes, Mr. Tolar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.44,0:25:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟透的建议书 重新草议调回离岸资金的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hell of a proposal. Just redraft this part on repatriation of offshore funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.11,0:25:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明天我就要 - 明天？我要多一个星期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l need it tomorrow. - Tomorrow?. l need another week.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.45,0:25:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，你和我 明天要飞去开曼见葛先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Can't have it. You and l fly to the Caymans tomorrow to see Mr. Capps.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.99,0:26:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是有执业考试！ - 你回来时就有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- But the bar exam! - lt'll be here when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.23,0:26:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我留下来吗？ 你可想吃三文治？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Shall l stay, Mr. McDeere? Would you like a sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.40,0:26:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，妮娜，谢谢 你回家吧，晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No, l'm fine, Nina. Thank you. You go on home. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.52,0:26:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这里有什么好吃？ - 我只要了咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- So, what's good here? - l'm just having coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.93,0:26:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要一客牛排三文治 - 两客牛排三文治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'm going with a steak sandwich. - Two steak sandwiches on rolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.66,0:26:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两客牛排三文治\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Two steak sandwiches on a roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.43,0:26:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是彭林骆律师行的？ - 是的，你怎么...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You with Bendini, Lambert & Locke? - Yeah, how did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.74,0:26:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉，我有点... - 他们令你忙得没命？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Sorry, l'm just a little... - Are they working you to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是那样对待新的初级律师 我刚加入他们...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They do that with new associates. l've just been with them now--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.44,0:27:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八个星期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}-Eight weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.06,0:27:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，两位，我有点率直\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sorry, guys, l'm just a little punchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.26,0:27:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那间公司看来对健康有害 - 迫你干那么多钟数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- That firm looks like a health hazard. - Hours they make you keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.10,0:27:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要你做那种工作 - 郭文迪和何约瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Kind of work they make you do. - Kozinski and Hodges.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.00,0:27:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林罗拔和高爱丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Bob Lamm and Alice Krauss.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.67,0:27:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不足十年内 四十一个律师中死了四个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's four dead lawyers out of 41 in less than ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.31,0:27:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是未够四十五岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}None of them over the age of 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.78,0:27:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我听闻的最大笔的保险赔偿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Beats the hell out of any life insurance tables l've ever heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.42,0:27:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.02,0:27:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你，那些三文治我们拿走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Could we get those sandwiches to go, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.73,0:27:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能会再见的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We'll probably see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.93,0:27:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（高爱丽，1948- 1988）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.31,0:28:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（林罗拔）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.31,0:28:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（何约瑟，1951- 1992）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.69,0:28:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（请输入问题： 高爱丽）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.00,0:28:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（搜寻中）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.57,0:28:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（郭文迪）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.25,0:28:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（在开曼遇害的 孟菲斯市律师）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.09,0:29:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（在开曼一次不明爆炸事件的 几名遇害人）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.10,0:29:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（潜水船长颜莱利的尸体 下落不明）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.89,0:29:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汽车抛锚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Car wouldn't start.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.80,0:29:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被困在交通意外中 有十二辆汽车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l got caught in this incredible accident. Twelve cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.34,0:29:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是十三辆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Maybe 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.18,0:29:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一辆还有个孕妇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And there was a pregnant woman in one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.22,0:29:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要帮忙接生，是个女婴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l had to help deliver the baby. lt was a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.26,0:30:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说会替她取名艾佩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They said they're gonna name her Abigail.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.86,0:30:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别生气！ 你以为我 干嘛工作得这个样子？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Fuck! Why do you think l'm working like this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.77,0:30:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 因为我想你拥有... - 等一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Because l want you to have-- - Wait a minute. Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.34,0:30:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有要求过什么 除了我们在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l never asked for anything, except for us to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.10,0:30:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想给你，你为了嫁给我而放弃的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But I want to give it to you.l want to give you everything you gave up to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.45,0:30:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住口！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.89,0:30:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它很甜蜜 我知道那是了不起的邂逅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's sweet. l know. lt's some kind of courtship -
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.66,0:30:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不需要那些 只要有时送花给我就可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- but l don't need all that. Just bring me flowers sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.31,0:30:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你整晚在忙什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What were you working on all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是...一些事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Just... stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.03,0:31:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦利要我负责到开曼的差事 想吃蛋吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...Avery's got me doing for the Cayman trip. Hey, wanna have some eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.96,0:31:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我吃了蛋 - 想光脱脱的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l had some eggs. - Want to have some naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.99,0:31:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不明白 你打动我的是什么吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You don't even know what moves me about you, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.53,0:31:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白你要什么 但你和我都是身不由己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know what you want, but it's not for me. lt's not even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.80,0:31:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.77,0:31:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,富有人家谈做穷人很容易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's easy for somebody rich to talk about being poor -
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.87,0:31:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像一头苍蝇烦着你 你只要把它挥走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- like it's some fly bothering you. You just wave it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.94,0:31:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不关富有或贫穷的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This isn't about rich or poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.71,0:32:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有关弄好 十辆平治房车也弄不好的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This is about trying to fix something that won't get fixed with 10 Mercedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.02,0:32:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩，那样不公平！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's not fair, Abby. That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.65,0:32:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是有关 一个在停车场干活的母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This is about a mother in a trailer park.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.56,0:32:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和一个你假装没有的哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And a brother you pretend you don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.36,0:32:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.40,0:32:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 跟着我，别过度呼吸 - 葛善礼又怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Just follow me. Don't overbreathe. - What about Sonny Capps?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.94,0:32:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我觉得我们有压力 - 我们有很大的压力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l thought we're under pressure. - We're under tremendous pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.61,0:32:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们不在见银行前 潜一下水，就没机会了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf we don't get this dive in before the bank, we can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.95,0:32:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能在二十四小时内 潜水和飞行的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You can't dive and then fly within 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.95,0:32:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎可以在意外发生后 这么快就潜水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't see how you can dive so soon after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.69,0:32:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们根本不知道 郭文迪和何约瑟发生什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We don't even know what happened to Kozinski and Hodges.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.99,0:32:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上周发生了空难 我们也不是坐船来的吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}There was a plane crash last week. We didn't take a boat, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.76,0:32:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（颜氏开曼潜水公司）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.00,0:32:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,善礼，那样真荒谬 让我们坐下来谈一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's ridiculous, Sonny. Let him sit down with you for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.30,0:32:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.57,0:33:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋付不够百分之五的税 还要开除我们...凯悦酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Son of a bitch pays less than 5%/ tax and wants to fire us. The Hyatt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.84,0:33:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这新的计划是很进取的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This new plan is very aggressive, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.11,0:33:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可以把你的税款推迟数年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And it defers all your tax liability for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.71,0:33:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还可以即时开始 - 对不起甜心，我现在不能谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- And you could start right away. - l'm sorry, darling. l can't talk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.79,0:33:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只可以推迟税款？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}These taxes are only deferred, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.86,0:33:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,税款的未来值会是现值的一半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The future value of the tax dollars will be half their present value.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.86,0:33:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁说的？ - 选举之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Who says? - After the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.66,0:33:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否在告诉我 四年后谁入主白宫？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Are you telling me who'll be in the White House the next 4 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.43,0:33:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是很宝贵的资料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's valuable information!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.97,0:33:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这个... - 杜先生有一个计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Well-- - Mr. Tolar has a plan that--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.01,0:33:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁入主白宫 都可以符合你的需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...that meets all your needs. Whoever's in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.08,0:33:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让他告诉我吧 - 他在尝试着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Let him tell me. - He's been trying to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.48,0:33:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的你是谁？ 他的律师还是我的律师？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Who the fuck are you? His lawyer or mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.68,0:33:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁都不是 - 他妈的你在干嘛？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Neither one, sir. - What the fuck are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.42,0:33:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,善礼...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sonny...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.75,0:33:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是律师行唯一的重点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're not the firm's only concern here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.05,0:33:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们安排你跟别的客户交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We put you into deals with other clients -
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.66,0:33:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能不想把他们的关系 向外间的律师透露\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- who may not wish to expose their relationships to outside attorneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.06,0:34:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顾问，你听到吗？ 那是个变相恐吓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You hear that, Counsellor?. That's a veiled threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.30,0:34:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你是指我们在芝加哥的朋友 我付律师费时他们没有攫利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf you mean our friends in Chicago, they don't profit when l pay you fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.20,0:34:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们却问我要钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You mak e money when I pay you fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.54,0:34:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们从我的生意中赚钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They profit from my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.37,0:34:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们赚到钱 他们懒得理会谁替我报税\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And as long as they're making money,they don't give a flying fuck who does my taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.68,0:34:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不认识我，我是个好人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You don't know me. l'm a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.18,0:34:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你替我削减一百万元 我就不会伤害你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You lose a million bucks for me. l'm not gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.85,0:34:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不会打断你的腿 - 善礼...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'm not gonna break your legs. - Sonny...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.92,0:34:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别扯开话题吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...let's not get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.92,0:34:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What did l say?.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.96,0:34:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我说了什么？ - 也许是你没有说的那句话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What did l say!? - Maybe it's what you didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.43,0:34:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我没有说的” 我没有说什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}'What l didn't say''. What didn't l say?.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.10,0:34:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你 - 杜先生给了你一个计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Thank you. - Mr. Tolar gave you a schedule that -
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.97,0:34:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直保证你既不用交税 又没有风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- virtually guarantees you zero tax with zero risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.80,0:34:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的股票基本 就是分期付款的帐面数目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The basis of your stock would be the face amount of the installment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.44,0:34:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那股票不会有价值，即使这样 它已被扣除又抵销收入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The stock would have no value. Even so, it's deducted and offsets income.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.91,0:34:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你有一张银行可承兑的 信用状，也可以全数推迟税款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You defer your tax in full even though you have a bankable LC.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.55,0:34:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 推迟到几时？ - 你在乎什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Deferred 'til when? - What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.15,0:34:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论几时 它仍是你最好的免息贷款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Whenever it is, it's still the best interest-free loan you'll ever get.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.25,0:34:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么最糟的就是 我很久之后才交税\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So, the worst is l pay my taxes much, much later?.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.69,0:35:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，最糟的是明年 他们快要堵塞那个漏洞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No, the worst thing is next year, they're gonna close the loophole -
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.30,0:35:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不抓着这份建议书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and if you haven't grabbed this proposal -
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.33,0:35:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就会感到有如大祸临头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- you'll feel like you've been fucked with an enormous elephant dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.87,0:35:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么肯定？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You know that for a fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.11,0:35:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢“门生” 这个词吗？ 我从来没有门生，你做过吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You like the word ''protege''? l never had one. You ever been one?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.45,0:35:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是A，你是B，就在隔壁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm ''A'', you're ''B'', right next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.45,0:35:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦利，谁在芝加哥？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Avery, who's in Chicago?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.79,0:35:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迟一点再说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We'll get to all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.03,0:35:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦...洗个脸后过来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The hell with it. Clean up and come on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.60,0:35:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应得一顿丰富晚餐和消遣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You earned a good dinner and a night out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.23,0:36:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的儿子死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l lost my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.14,0:36:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我怀疑过有问题 就会大叫是血腥谋杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l would've screamed bloody murder if l thought something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.47,0:36:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颜先生，你说得对，对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're right, Mr. Abanks. l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.21,0:36:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没得埋藏 只有一块石头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Nothing to bury even. Just a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.78,0:36:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一直找不到他 和另外那两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They never did find him or the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.05,0:36:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么另外两个人？ - 租船的另外两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What other two? - The other two who split the charter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.76,0:36:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的朋友们和另外两个人 - 律师？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Your friends and two other guys. - Lawyers?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.56,0:36:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们穿了泳衣，付现金\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They were in swim suits. They paid cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.63,0:36:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们是美国人吗？ - 很难说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Were they American? - Could have been anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.00,0:36:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个很魁梧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}One was ''squat heavy'.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.37,0:36:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个蓄着长金发，几乎是 白色的，有古怪的蓝眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The other guy had long blond hair, almost white, with weird blue eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.85,0:37:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 文俊？ - 什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Mitch? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.95,0:37:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在冰箱拿一支 “红带” 喝吧 我会有点慢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Grab a Red Stripe out of the fridge. l'm a little slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.29,0:37:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你慢慢吧 - 我想装扮得像你一样帅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Take your time. - l'm trying to look as pretty as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.23,0:37:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定我可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...which l'm convinced l can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.90,0:37:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是要花多一点时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Just takes me a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.54,0:37:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有吃的东西吗？ - 冰箱旁边有些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Anything to munch on? - There's some stuff next to the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.01,0:37:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有锁的 用我给你的那串钥匙吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's got a lock on it. Use that key from the ring l gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.02,0:37:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看到吗？ - 看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You see it? - Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.30,0:37:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（芝加哥 摩洛哥公司）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.44,0:38:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到东西吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.68,0:38:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（高爱丽，摩洛哥公司 芝加哥）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.38,0:38:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着，葛是强硬的人 也是个大话精\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Listen... Capps is a tough guy, but he's also a blowhard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.22,0:38:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（由郭文迪、林罗拔负责）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.62,0:38:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吹嘘自己交游广阔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Loves to give the impression that he's connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.52,0:38:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为那样很有派头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Thinks it's glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.79,0:38:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说过一些话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He said a couple of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.53,0:38:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快要考执业试了 这是一条选择题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're about to take the bar exam. Here's a multiple choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.90,0:38:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避税和逃税的分别是：\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The difference between tax avoidance and tax evasion is -
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.18,0:38:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A，税局说什么就什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- A) whatever the lRS says -
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.71,0:38:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B，一个聪明的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- B) a smart lawyer -
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.25,0:38:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C，十年监禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- C) ten years in prison; -
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.79,0:38:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D，以上全部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- D) all the above.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.65,0:38:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,税务律师跟法律没有关系 它是一场游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Being a tax lawyer's got nothing to do with the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.10,0:39:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们教有钱人怎样玩它 让他们可以继续富有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We teach the rich how to play it, so they can stay rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.40,0:39:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,税局改变条例 我们可以继续借教他们来赚钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The lRS changes the rules, so we can keep getting rich, teaching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.97,0:39:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一场游戏，要玩得十分精明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's a game. One you just played very, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.71,0:39:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的啤酒呢？ - 我还是等喝甜酒好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Where's your beer?. - l decided to wait for the rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.85,0:39:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听说这里的很好喝 - 这里所有的东西都好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l hear it's good down here. - Everything's good down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.35,0:39:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应值得尝尽它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You deserve a taste of all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.73,0:39:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我们来到这个岛 我们可以做些事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Since we're here on this island, there's things we can do on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.97,0:39:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原始的事，来吧，是你应得的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You know, primitive things. Come on, you deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.31,0:39:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无意令你难堪 但这事不会发生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't mean to hurt your feelings, but this isn't gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.42,0:39:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你告诉我的朋友 我返回公寓去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Would you tell my friend l went back to the condo?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.69,0:40:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Thanks, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.88,0:40:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？不要紧的，等一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Are you all right? That's OK. Just wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.62,0:41:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一会，我可以看一下吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Wait a minute. Can l look at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.96,0:41:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.99,0:41:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我扭伤过很多足踝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No, but l sprained a lot of ankles.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.77,0:41:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多是我的足踝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mostly mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.54,0:41:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该用冰敷着，还该报警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You should ice this. You should also report that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.35,0:41:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的男朋友？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That was your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.69,0:41:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That was for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.84,0:41:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不是要包扎好它吗？ - 对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Aren't you going to finish? - l'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.38,0:42:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 事情是... - 跟我无关\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- The thing that's-- - ...got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.76,0:42:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是不是太紧？ - 不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- ls this too tight? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在旅行社工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l work in a travel agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.94,0:42:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想觉得像那些人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l wanted to feel like all those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.01,0:42:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐头等机位和穿漂亮衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...with first class tickets and pretty clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.69,0:42:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想觉得...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l guess l wanted to feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.99,0:42:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像有钱人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.41,0:43:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才觉得有钱？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How much would it take to feel rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.00,0:43:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.68,0:43:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才觉得安全？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How much would it take to feel safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.10,0:43:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.10,0:43:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你令我觉得安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You made me feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.68,0:44:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可否陪我一会儿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Will you stay with me for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.01,0:45:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如你下午放假吧，你应得的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why don't you take the afternoon off? You deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.64,0:45:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪你那位漂亮的太太...该死 我忘了她昨晚打过电话来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Spend it with that pretty wife of yours. Shit, l forgot. She phoned last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.82,0:46:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你对她说什么？ - 说你在海滩散步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What did you tell her?. - That you were walking on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.65,0:46:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我是的 - 我猜对了，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l was. - l guessed right then. Didn't l?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.76,0:46:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦先生 请在交叉的位置上签名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK, Mr. McDeere. Sign where the ''X'' is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.70,0:46:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有在记号上签首个字母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And initial where it's marked.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.59,0:46:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“绅士”杂志的人来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Well, well... The man from Gentlemen's Quarterly.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.53,0:46:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 雷，你好吗？ - 蛮好，你呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- How are you doing, Ray?. - Pretty fair. How's yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.37,0:46:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很久了 - 不要紧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's a long time. - lt's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.94,0:47:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我变成一个有忍耐力的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l've become a patient man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.65,0:47:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强自己 要不是我在这里，我也不愿来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Don't beat yourself up, kid. lf l wasn't here, l wouldn't want to be here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.86,0:47:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有没有和妈联络？ - 几个月前有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You ever talk to Ma? - A few months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.37,0:47:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还是跟着那个家伙？ - 都是那个家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Still with the same guy?. - They're all the same guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.48,0:47:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 念完法律没有？ - 念完了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- So, you finished law school? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.95,0:47:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那套西装很有派头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That suit's a dead giveaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.69,0:47:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在华尔街找到工作了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Did you get a job on Wall Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.96,0:47:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你常说... - 我没有，我只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You always said-- - No, l'm not. l just--
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.07,0:47:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我加入了一间 在孟菲斯的律师行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l went with a firm across the river in Memphis.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.04,0:48:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 孟菲斯？ - 雷...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Memphis? - Hey, Ray...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.07,0:48:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我进了哈佛而你进了监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Wouldn't it be funny if l went to Harvard and you went to jail -
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.81,0:48:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最终我们周围也是骗子 这可笑吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and we both ended up surrounded by crooks?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.65,0:48:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛善礼很兴奋，麦就眼花撩乱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sonny Capps is thrilled. McDeere was dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.98,0:48:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该取消力万去华盛顿的 税务研讨会，改派文俊去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We ought to pull Lamar out of that tax seminar in D.C. Send Mitch instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.09,0:48:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他坐公司的飞机 比尧，可有问题？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Let him take the jet. Any problem with that, Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.36,0:48:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题，到目前为止 那个小子真的是可以预料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No problem. So far, the kid's been real predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.33,0:48:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你对了一半 也需要人帮助的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf you're even half right, you're gonna need some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.80,0:48:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩觉得怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What does Abby think?.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.84,0:48:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有告诉她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l haven't told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.91,0:48:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想...我不想它是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l guess... l guess l don't want it to be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.14,0:48:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉艾佩时才算是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Nothing's real until I tell it to Abby.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.89,0:48:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有个坐牢的哥哥 怎会找到工作？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How'd you ever land a job with a brother in the joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.67,0:49:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧，换了是我也会那样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's OK. l'd a done the same thing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.91,0:49:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸去世之后 多年来你一直照顾我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're always around for me, Ray. All those years after Dad died.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.41,0:49:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会那样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'd a done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.82,0:49:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会对这里的人说 我有个念哈佛的弟弟吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Think l'd ever tell guys around here l got a brother at Harvard?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.49,0:49:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你去见我一个朋友 他名叫卢毅迪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Listen, l want you to see a friend of mine. His name's Eddie Lomax.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.99,0:49:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在小石城当私家侦探 是个前任警员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's a private investigator in Little Rock. Ex-cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.37,0:49:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有什么我可以为你做？ - 有，帮我离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Anything l can do for you? - Sure. Get me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.97,0:49:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去哪里？ - 可以看见大片天空的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Where to? - Anywhere l'll see a whole lot of sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.18,0:49:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以熬过那些日子 甚至吃得下那些食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can get through the days. l even eat the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.12,0:49:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那样怀念天空真是奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's amazing how much l miss the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.63,0:50:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有试过插了掣 却忘了放水进去？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Ever plug one of these in only you forgot to put the water in?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.10,0:50:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有 - 可知道会有什么事发生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- No. - You know what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.67,0:50:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不知道 - 电灯全熄了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- No. - The lights go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.88,0:50:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打过电话来后 他一直渴望见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's been dying to see you since you called.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.21,0:50:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是看见那个！ 谭美！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's what l saw. Tammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.92,0:50:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卢先生可以见你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. Lomax will see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.99,0:50:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦先生 我几乎跟你一起去念法律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. McDeere. l practically went to law school with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.23,0:50:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三年臭气冲天的日子里 雷每天都说起你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Ray talked about you every stinkin' day for three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.68,0:50:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对你说我曾是他的仓友？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}I was his cellmate, he must have told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.68,0:50:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可有说是决定强奸罪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Did he tell you,by the way, it was statutory rape?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.12,0:50:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那时十七岁，看似二十五岁 我判了一至四年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}She was 1 7. Look ed 25. I got one to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.20,0:50:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来，坐下 要代糖？牛奶？沙糖？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sit down. Come on. Sweet 'n Low?. Dairy cream? Sugar?.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.91,0:50:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你谈一下生意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l got some business l'd like to go over with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.38,0:50:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的，我欠你哥哥一命 - 我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Good. l owe your brother my life. - l'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.31,0:51:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，亲爱的 那是我的秘书，她很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Thank you, dear. That's my secretary. She is terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.12,0:51:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她嫁了个笨蛋，是个货车司机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}She's got a nutcase for a husband. He's a truckdriver -
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.86,0:51:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他搬来这里想接近猫王故居 他以为自己是猫王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- who moved here to be close to Graceland. He thinks he's Elvis.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.23,0:51:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可知道他叫什么？ 就是艾维斯韩亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What do you think his name is? lt's Elvis. Elvis Aaron Henfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.30,0:51:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做这份工作，遇到很多怪事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l run across strange things in this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.53,0:51:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一些我不会用喷漆 在天桥上喷出来的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Things l would never spray paint on an overpass.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.27,0:51:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么为你效劳？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Now, what can l do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.84,0:51:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真是个惊喜！ - 韦利！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What a nice surprise! - Avery!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.71,0:51:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们不用打扰你的 - 相信我，没有打扰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- They didn't have to disturb you. - Believe me, it's no bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.22,0:51:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来找文俊 妮娜说他整个下午都不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l was just looking for Mitch. Nina says he hasn't been in all afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.22,0:51:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有叫她去找你的 他没有跟你一起回来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l didn't mean for her to call you. Didn't he come back with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.16,0:51:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要老实告诉你 这不是我专长的范畴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll be honest with you. This is not my area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.30,0:51:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但你觉得有可能吗？ - 什么事都有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- But you think it's possible? - Anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.27,0:51:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对你说，如果那两个 在牛排餐馆的人是联邦密探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll tell you one thing. lf those guys at the steak joint were Feds -
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.11,0:51:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就要警惕了 他们不会在乎你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- you'd better watch out. They don't give a damn about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.04,0:52:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这里有几个很火光的丈夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l get some pretty pissed off husbands in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.75,0:52:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面，你公司的律师们 看来很易发生事故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}On the other hand, the lawyers at your firm seem ''accident-prone''.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.99,0:52:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，我看看可以找到什么吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK, l'll see what l can find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.26,0:52:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好还是由我找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You had better let me call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.87,0:52:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的令我想起你的哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You sure remind me of your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.40,0:52:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷很快会被假释了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Ray comes up for parole in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.01,0:52:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说可以持续下去的 你认为怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He says that he can last it. What do you think?.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.88,0:52:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人可以熬得过 州政府判他的刑期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}There's guys who can do all the hard time the state gives 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.48,0:52:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论雷判了多久 他也熬不下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Whatever Ray had, he used up to get this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.70,0:52:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我以为你不在家 - 为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l didn't think you were home. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.40,0:53:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有车 - 我拿了去维修\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- No car. - l took it in for service.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.61,0:53:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是吗？ - 韦利送我回家的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Did you? - Avery brought me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.78,0:53:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我去过公司找你 - 我不在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Went to the office looking for you. - l wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.41,0:53:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的 我甚至在你的台底找过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Apparently not. l even looked under your desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.69,0:53:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦利说你去了孟菲斯 州立大学的法律图书馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Avery told me you were at M.S.U. at the law library.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.69,0:53:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 韦利说的？ - 韦利说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Avery did? - Avery did.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.16,0:53:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但当我看到你的车在停车场时 他却有点紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But when l spotted your car in the parking lot, it made him kind of edgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.20,0:53:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦利不太清楚我在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Avery didn't exactly know where l was.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.50,0:53:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能以为你跟别个女人一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Probably thought you were with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.51,0:53:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我去了看雷 - 雷？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l went to see Ray. - Ray?.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.75,0:53:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 - 就是那样，这么久之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Yeah. - Just like that. After all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.72,0:53:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对，我很愚蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're right. l've been stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.86,0:53:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在周六可以跟你去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'd have gone with you on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.99,0:54:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有想起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know. God, I just wasn't. . .I wasn't thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.14,0:54:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.62,0:54:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想令我好过一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He tried to make it easy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.29,0:54:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ls he OK?.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.99,0:54:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定要得到假释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's gotta get that parole.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.53,0:54:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可想试一件事？ 我们把本子弃掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Do you want to try something? Let's put the books away.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.83,0:54:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假装回到我们以前 那间简陋的公寓，身无分文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Pretend we're back in our old beat-up apartment, broke -
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.17,0:54:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在口袋里找遗下来的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and we find some money we forgot in pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.88,0:54:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 叫薄饼外卖 - 喝啤酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- We'll send out for pizza-- - ...drink beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.38,0:54:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 “巨星搜索” 谁晓得日后会如何？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Watch ''Star Search''. Who knows where it will lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.68,0:55:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的老婆 - 她在克利夫兰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Your wife. - She's in Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.08,0:55:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}She lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.45,0:55:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不接电话的吗？ - 你不敲门的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Don't you answer your phone? - Don't you knock?.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.79,0:55:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的秘书呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Where's your secretary?.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.53,0:55:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 出去了 - 她留下了一支点着的香烟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Out. - She left a cigarette burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.57,0:55:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是那样的 一小时后回来预约吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}She does that. Come back in an hour and make an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.47,0:55:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 干嘛要烦？我们都来了 - 我很忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Why bother?. We're here. - l'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.58,0:55:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 忙什么？ - 我在修脚甲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Doing what? - l'm getting a pedicure.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.75,0:55:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关你何事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What's it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.56,0:56:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这将会令你很糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This is gonna turn out badly for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.79,0:56:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们可以做得没有痛楚 干嘛要查问有关死了的律师？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But we can make it painless. Why the questions about dead lawyers?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.17,0:56:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么死了的律师？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What dead lawyers?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.67,0:56:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁雇用你那样做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Who hired you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.11,0:56:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK... OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.55,0:56:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我想一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Just let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.69,0:56:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是...乐坛天王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}His name was Julio lglesias.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.13,0:56:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.70,0:56:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Great! Just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.14,0:56:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还想问他几条问题吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You wanna ask him a few questions now?.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.33,0:57:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（华盛顿税务学会）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.70,0:57:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是一份周详的建议书 我觉得它很高明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l think this is a carefully balanced proposal. l think it's high-minded -
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.81,0:57:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也很公正\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and l think it's fair-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.84,0:57:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是说，它有一些 令所有人不快的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ln other words, it's got something in it to offend everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.21,0:57:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你们想探讨我的看法 我们从引书的第一页开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf you want to follow along with me, we begin on page 1 of the lntroduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.42,0:57:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻阅1986年税局条例 第7046段...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We'll review Section 704b of the lRS Code of 1986.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.82,0:57:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（本地私家侦探 在办公室中枪死亡）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.13,0:57:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（午饭时坐穿梭车到映照池 林肯纪念堂）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.60,0:57:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（是时候要谈一下了 联邦密探戴韦恩）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.14,0:58:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依据联营公司合伙人的利益 除非...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...in accordance with partners' interests in the partnership, unless -
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.24,0:58:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些分配符合经济效益 而这些利益...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- those allocations satisfy the economic effect most easily satisfied -
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.68,0:58:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借着作出安全储备 就像容易达致...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- by taking advantage of the safe harbour provisions set forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.10,0:58:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟，走下梯级到池那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Brother, go down the steps towards the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.67,0:58:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟，拿着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Here you go, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.84,0:58:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“围墙之声”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}'Voices from the Wall''.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.02,0:58:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 卢毅迪是谁杀的？ - 坐到长椅上那个男人旁边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Who killed Eddie Lomax?. - Sit next to the man on the bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.05,0:59:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦先生，很感谢你到来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l appreciate your coming, Mr. McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.08,0:59:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你文俊吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll call you Mitch, if l may.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.21,0:59:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫胡鼎廷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}My name is Voyles. Denton Voyles.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.21,0:59:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是司法部人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm with the Department of J ustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.59,0:59:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卢毅迪发生了什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What happened to Eddie Lomax?.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.79,0:59:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们调查了彭林骆律师行四年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We've been investigating Bendini, Lambert & Locke for 4 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.87,0:59:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从没有律师活着离开你的公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No lawyer's ever left your law firm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.44,0:59:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有两个想离开就死了 两个准备离开的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Two tried to leave. They were killed. Two were about to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.57,0:59:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.01,0:59:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信你家里被装上偷听器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We have reason to believe that your house is bugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.25,0:59:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你几个电话 和办公室也被人偷听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Your phones are tapped. Your office is wired.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.45,0:59:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能跟踪你，我们交谈时 他们可能也在华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They may follow you. They may be here in D.C. as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.53,1:00:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是否说我的生命... - 你知道，你的生命危在旦夕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Are you saying my life is-- - Your life, as you know it, is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.57,1:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的律师行 是芝加哥莫鲁图犯罪家族的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Your law firm is the sole legal representative -
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.14,1:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一法律代表 也称为黑手党、黑帮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- of the Morolto crime family in Chicago, aka the Mafia. The Mob.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.15,1:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不相信 - 他们借贩毒、赌博和卖淫...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l don't believe it. - They set up legitimate businesses -
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.01,1:00:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得来的肮脏钱经营合法生意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- with dirty money from drugs, gambling, prostitution.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.48,1:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是调到海外的现金 你相信它吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}All cash, all moved offshore. You believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.52,1:00:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此你在开曼跟颜道文谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's why you talked to Abanks in the Caymans.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.46,1:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此你叫卢毅迪侦查 而令他遇害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's why you got Eddie Lomax asking questions that got him killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.66,1:00:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们百分之三十的客户 是合法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Maybe 30%/ of their clients are legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.47,1:00:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们聘用一个新丁 向他大洒金钱，买车买屋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They bring in a new rookie, throw money at him, buy the car, the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.37,1:00:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两、三年后 你的孩子们在私立学校念书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}After a couple of years, your kids are in private school.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.11,1:00:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你习惯了过好生活时 他们便对你说出真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}When you're used to the ''good life'', they tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.92,1:01:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 公司里每个合伙人...？ - 公司里每个合伙人都知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Every partner in the firm--? - Every partner in the firm knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.39,1:01:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怀疑大部分的初级律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We suspect most of the associates.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.03,1:01:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你们不提出起诉 把它一网打尽？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why don't you get indictments and bust it all up?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.90,1:01:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要找个内应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We have to have somebody on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.10,1:01:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要看到合约 客户银行记录、公司成立法规\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We need to see contracts, clients' bank records, articles of incorporation.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.01,1:01:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 等一等，你以为我... - 你可以说不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Wait a minute. You think l-- - You can say no.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.11,1:01:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会捣破这间公司的 你会跟其他人一同入狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We're gonna break this firm. You'll go to jail along with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.69,1:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事会发生的，相信我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt'll happen, son. Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.29,1:01:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为何我不能离开？ - 郭文迪和何约瑟试过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Why can't l just leave? - Kozinski and Hodges tried to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.49,1:01:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你考虑一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You have to think this over.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.03,1:01:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时，你和艾佩 要表现得一切如常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Meanwhile, you and Abby have to behave as if everything is normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.34,1:02:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跟任何人讨论这件事 但要作个决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Don't discuss this with anyone. But make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.45,1:02:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮助我们 我们会令你物有所值\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You help us. We'll make it worth your while.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.08,1:02:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 物有所值？ - 你仍可以过好的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Worth my while? - You can still have a good life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.19,1:02:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说在保护证人计划之下？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You mean in a witness protection programme?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.80,1:02:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？我要过着 另一个人的生活？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How?. l live somebody else's life?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.17,1:02:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去个偏僻的地方？ 一天我开动汽车时它就爆炸？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Some nowhere place? One day l start my car and it explodes?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.51,1:02:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不必那个样子的 - 我不大要什么生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Doesn't have to be that way. - l don't need much of a life, Voyles -
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.28,1:02:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但却要属于我的 - 你现在有吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- but it has to be mine. - ls that what you got now, son?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.99,1:02:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要回到研讨会了 戴伦斯会代表我们谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You oughta get back to the seminar. Tarrance negotiates on our behalf.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.59,1:02:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你绕过纪念堂回去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why don't you wander back past the Memorial?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.01,1:03:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以在孟菲斯任何时间找我 你有我的手提电话号码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You can call me in Memphis any time day or night. You have my mobile.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.24,1:03:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我弄清楚这件事 我从律师行偷取档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Let me get this straight. l steal files from the firm, -
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.85,1:03:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给联邦调查局 指证我的同事，送他们进监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- pass them to the FBl, testify against my colleagues. Send them to jail...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.15,1:03:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们把你拖下水了 - 泄露享有特权的资料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- They suckered you into this. - ...Reveal privileged information -
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.76,1:03:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,违反律师与当事人之间的信任 令我吊销律师资格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- that violates attorney-client confidences, get me disbarred -
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.96,1:03:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再在公开法庭上指证黑手党\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- then testify in open court against the Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.66,1:03:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 文俊，可惜... - 我问你一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Unfortunately, Mitch-- - Let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.90,1:03:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是发疯了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Are you out of your fucking mind!?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.37,1:03:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要多久才发现 卢毅迪的仓友是麦雷？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How long before they find out Lomax's cellmate was Ray McDeere?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.08,1:03:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道后 你认为他们会怎样对他？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And when they do, what do you think they'll do to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.21,1:03:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 无论何处，他们谁也抓得到 - 你们可以做什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- They can get to anyone anywhere. - What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.68,1:03:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥快将被假释，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Your brother comes up for parole soon, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.35,1:03:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我们合作 我保证委员会会很感激你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You cooperate with us, l'll guarantee the board will be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.69,1:04:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则...你也明白 那些假释聆讯是怎样吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Otherwise... You know what those parole hearings are like.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.93,1:04:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以是模拟两可的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt could go either way.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.03,1:04:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要回家，送我回公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Forget about home, driver. Take me to the firm.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.70,1:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦先生，你不能进去 - 马上找所有的人！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Mr. McDeere, you can't go in-- - Call everybody. Right now!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.67,1:04:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我在说长途电话，我有两... - 马上！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'm on overseas. l've got two-- - Right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.77,1:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚与联邦调查局聊过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l just had a little chat with the FBl.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.68,1:04:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们没有威迫你吗？ - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- They didn't try to coerce you? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.05,1:04:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们没有给你钱？ - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- They didn't offer you money?. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.69,1:05:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们要你再联络他们吗？ - 为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- They want you to recontact them? - What for?.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.83,1:05:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们究竟要什么？ - 那些秘密档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Exactly what did they want? - The secret files.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.67,1:05:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁最后用过那些秘密档案？ 洛斯？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Who had those secret files last? Royce?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.11,1:05:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用过？洛斯？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You have them, Royce?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.18,1:05:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我给了你的 - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l gave them to you. - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.15,1:05:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还说何约瑟和郭文迪 是被谋杀的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They also suggested that Hodges and Kozinski were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.65,1:05:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些混蛋！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Those sons of bitches!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.89,1:05:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该提出控告 这简直是骚扰！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We ought to build a case and sue. This is pure harassment!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.50,1:05:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And that was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.29,1:05:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说了这些？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That was everything that was said?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.67,1:05:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据我记忆... 它不是一次连续的谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}As far as l can remember... lt wasn't a sequential conversation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.14,1:05:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 夹杂着叫喊，大多是我的 - 文俊！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- There was yelling, mostly by me. - Mitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.24,1:05:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们经常都跟政府对抗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We're always doing battle with the government.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.85,1:06:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是司法部就是税局 我们每次都打赢他们！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf it isn't the Justice Department, it's the lRS. We beat them everytime!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.25,1:06:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们因此怀恨在心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And they hate us for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.96,1:06:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们抓不到我们 就来对付新人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They can't get to us, so they pick on somebody new.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.63,1:06:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们叫你去犯法 对他们毫无损失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They invite you to break the law. Doesn't cost them anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.46,1:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你会损失一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But it costs you everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.20,1:06:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你担心这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't want you to worry about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.80,1:06:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况相当严重 我们会用合法途径处理它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's gotten serious enough. We'll have to get into it legally.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.27,1:06:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜唯一的问题是 这个小时入谁的帐？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l guess the only other question is： Who do we bill this hour to?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.38,1:06:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入联邦调查局怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How about the FBl?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.02,1:07:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想相信，真是奇怪 我刚才正在想你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can't believe that. That is so weird. l was just thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.46,1:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在外面烧树叶 你闻到吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Somebody's burning leaves outside. Did you smell it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.96,1:07:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我记起...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Reminded me of the time--
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.80,1:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你怕吵醒孩子们 我们是没有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hey, if you're afraid you'll wake the kids, we don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.47,1:08:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Abby!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.88,1:08:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Abby!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.62,1:08:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾佩！ - 不要说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Abby! Abby! - Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.02,1:08:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Don't tell me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.76,1:08:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.06,1:09:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在屋里说过 或者做过的每一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Every single thing we've said or done since we've been in that house.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.16,1:09:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间没有隐瞒的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Nothing has been between us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.90,1:09:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可否 今晚开车返回波士顿？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Can't we just drive back to Boston tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.34,1:09:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们需要一切 - 他们会找到我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- We'll leave everything. - They'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.34,1:09:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天你怎样回去上班？ 你对韦利说什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How do you go to work tomorrow?. What do you say to Avery?.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.68,1:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我只谈工作 - 发神经！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l talk about work. - That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.78,1:09:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我考虑过所有可行的办法 在这里，开曼、华盛顿...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l have thought of every possible way. Here, in the Caymans, in D.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.19,1:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们逃走，他们会 找到我们，也会害死雷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf we run, they find us. And it gets Ray killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.76,1:09:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但如果你作证... - 联调局会帮雷和保护我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- But if you testify-- - The FBl will help Ray and protect us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.93,1:09:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Protect what?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.96,1:09:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎样做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.53,1:09:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天回去开始影印档案 我没有选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Go in tomorrow and start to copy files. l don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.21,1:09:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊，你说什么？ 你会泄露当事人的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mitch, what are you saying? You'll be revealing clients' secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.85,1:09:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会被吊销资格 你终身也不能再当律师的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You'll be disbarred. You'll never practice law again your entire life.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.18,1:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你努力取得的一切 他们不能叫你那样做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Everything you've worked for. They can't ask you to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.32,1:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有叫我！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They are not asking!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.43,1:10:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天如常上班和回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We have to go to work and come home everyday -
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.11,1:10:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用猜疑那些墙壁...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- never wondering about the walls -
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.01,1:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 和偷听器 - 一于袖手旁观\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and the wires-- - And do nothing we want to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.16,1:10:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小王店的四川牛肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Szechuan Beef from Wong Boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.76,1:10:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得那是最后一次的欢笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That was the last time l remember laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.77,1:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天你总有一辆货车 塞着这条巷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Come on. Every single day one of your trucks blocks this alley.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.64,1:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别管我 - 你究竟想怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Leave me alone. - What's it gonna take, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.58,1:10:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你把这里变成你的停车场！ - 这条巷是你的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You use this as your parking lot. - Do you own this alley?.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.92,1:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（葛氏依达美公司 公司成立法规）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.08,1:11:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？天啊！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What the hell are you doing? Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.72,1:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 想影印一份... - 你要一个客户入帐密码的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Trying to make a copy. - You need a client billing code.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.16,1:11:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每次影印都有记录？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Everytime l make a copy, it's recorded?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.80,1:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么？ 自杀吗？ 叫妮娜做吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What are you trying to do? Kill yourself? Let Nina do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.10,1:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来一晚吧，可以吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Come down for one night. Can't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.41,1:11:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前都是值得的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt used to be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.28,1:12:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧...再见，歌莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Maybe next time. Bye, Cordelia.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.99,1:12:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是歌莉亚 - 你的太太\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}-That was Cordelia. - Your wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.76,1:12:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有一首同名的歌曲 - 我有关于葛氏信用状的构思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- From the song of the same name. - l have a few ideas about Capp LCs.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.53,1:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 几时再去开曼？ - 我？下星期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- When's the next Cayman trip? - For me? Next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.73,1:12:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让葛再见你一面？你疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Let Capps get another look at you? You're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.64,1:12:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过把每个构思写下来吧 我乐意邀功的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But write down every single thought. l'd be happy to take credit.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.61,1:12:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦先生？缪浩伦先生 打了两次电话来问他的帐单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. McDeere? Mr. Mulholland's called twice about his bills.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.31,1:12:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫缪先生拿他的帐单... 等一会，他不是在街尾吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Tell Mr. Mulholland to take his bill-- Wait, isn't he just up the street?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.59,1:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的，在红棉广场 - 告诉他我稍后去见他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Yes, in the Cotton Exchange. - Tell him l'll see him later.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.66,1:12:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可有在前街小食店 叫了一客煎蛋三文治？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Did you order a fried egg sandwich from the Front Street Deli?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.47,1:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Yes, l did. l did.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.77,1:13:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.54,1:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二元六角五分，收据在袋里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's $2.65. The receipt's in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.52,1:13:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收据在袋里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The receipt's in the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.37,1:13:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看见他们，他们看不到你 - 我当时在台底\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You saw 'em, but they didn't see you? - l was under the desk.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.85,1:13:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在吸尘 你要我说得露骨吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l was vacuuming the rug. Do you want me to draw you a diagram?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.55,1:13:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l loved him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.09,1:13:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谭美，我很难过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm sorry, Tammy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.90,1:14:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想知道 是谁雇用他来侦查死了的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They wanted to know who hired him to ask questions about dead lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.47,1:14:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有见到他们？ - 有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You actually saw them? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.08,1:14:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个很健硕，像个摔角手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}One guy was stocky, looked like a wrestler.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.41,1:14:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会终身拐着走路因为...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's gonna limp the rest of his life 'cause -
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.22,1:14:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毅迪用他台底那支手枪 射中他的膝头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Eddie hit him in the knee with that cannon under his desk.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.69,1:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个像患了白化病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The other guy was like an albino.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.89,1:14:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长而薄的头发，几乎是白色的 蓝蓝的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Long, thin hair, almost white. Dead blue eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.57,1:14:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的女房东说他们昨天来找我 所以我住进了一间六号旅馆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}My landlady said they came for me yesterday, so l went to a Motel 6.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.41,1:14:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会把雷跟毅迪扯在一起的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Listen, they're gonna match Eddie with Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.65,1:14:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候就会牵连到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}When they do, it'll lead to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.65,1:15:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你有什么不测 毅迪不会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't want anything bad to happen to you. Eddie wouldn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.26,1:15:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你跟我一样有难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So, you're in as much trouble as l am.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.36,1:15:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听过红棉广场吗？ 我要你到那里帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Heard of the Cotton Exchange? l need your help there, Tammy.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.27,1:15:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，文俊，我是戴比尧 公司保安组\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hi, there, Mitch. Bill Devasher, Firm Security.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.64,1:15:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骆先生和林先生告诉我 你跟联邦调查局有过节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Messrs. Locke and Lambert told me about your run-in with the FBl.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.08,1:15:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们可否谈一下？ - 我已经向他们说了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l wonder if we could have a little talk. - Actually, l told 'em everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.89,1:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，这不会花很多时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm sure you did. This won't take a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.53,1:15:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请上车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hop in.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.13,1:16:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊，这是一次汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So, Mitch, this is a debriefing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.10,1:16:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我清楚知道 你跟大伙儿说过什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know pretty much what you told the fellows. l got the picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.24,1:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的职责是要你了解情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's my job to give you the picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.38,1:16:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子，我关注的是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What l'm concerned about, son, is this.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.08,1:16:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联邦调查局追着你 因为他们有把握抓到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The FBl came after you 'cause they figured they'd get to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.18,1:16:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们为何那样想？ - 我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What made them think that? - l have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.69,1:16:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的职责就是要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}See, it's my job to have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.92,1:16:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能知道你太太 对你很重要，就那样做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They might know how important your wife is to you and choose that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.40,1:16:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How?.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.70,1:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦利说你在上周五下午放假\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Avery says last Friday you took the afternoon off.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.70,1:16:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他以为你可能跟别个女人一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He figures you might have been with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.34,1:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为何他以为... - 也许你被人跟踪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}-Why would he think-- - Maybe you were followed.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.61,1:17:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试想你的艾佩有一天走到信箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Here's your Abby one day walking to the mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.45,1:17:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期望收到她的家居杂志 或者邮购目录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Anticipating the arrival of her ''Redbook'' or a catalogue.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.29,1:17:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她却找到什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What does she find instead?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.46,1:17:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她找到心痛 爱情和信任都消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}She finds heartache, Mitch. The death of love and trust.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.40,1:17:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试想有一天她打开那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lmagine her one day opening that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.13,1:17:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开吧，看一看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Go ahead. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.94,1:17:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,震惊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Devastating.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.55,1:17:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不单只是做爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Not just screwing, Mitch -
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.88,1:17:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有各式性爱动作，花样百出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- but the kind of intimate acts, oral and whatnot -
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.69,1:17:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对一个年轻信任的妻子 特别难以...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- that could be particularly hard for a trusting young wife -
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.66,1:17:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去原谅和不可能忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- to forgive and impossible to forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.14,1:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是联邦调查局 用来威迫的手法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's the stuff the FBl uses for coercion, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.04,1:18:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要小心 我会尽力保护你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So, you watch yourself. l'll do the best l can to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.81,1:18:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道你会尽力保护律师行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And l know you'll do your best to protect the firm.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.12,1:18:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果联邦调查局向你施压\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So, if the FBl so much as spits in your direction -
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.99,1:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要尽快告诉我，好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- you'll let me know before it hits the ground, won't ya?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.46,1:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗，文俊？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Won't ya, Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.67,1:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利华想马上在图书馆见你 你去了哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Oliver wants to see you right now in the library. Where you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.14,1:18:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 让我先放下我的大衣 - 马上去，他在等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Let me just put my coat away. - Right now. He's been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.12,1:18:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你很聪明吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You think you're pretty smart, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.32,1:18:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来有人更聪明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We've been informed that somebody's smarter.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.26,1:19:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在执业考试中 拿不到最高的分数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You didn't get the highest score in the bar exam.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.17,1:19:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿到第二最高的分数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You got the second highest score.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.04,1:19:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hear, hear!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.68,1:19:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Nice one.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.31,1:19:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.68,1:19:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们找你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They called you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.72,1:19:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪过，法官大人，是我做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Guilty, your Honour. l did.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.82,1:19:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你光荣的一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's your moment of glory.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.93,1:19:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太太错过了我的一次 她十分后悔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You know, my wife missed mine. She never forgave herself.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.60,1:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不想你也一样 - 真是体贴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l didn't want that to happen to you. - That's very considerate.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.70,1:19:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 - 做得好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l thought so. - Well done. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.17,1:19:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊，了不起的成就\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Quite an achievement, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.81,1:19:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个单位不错，我会要了它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The space is just great. l'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.65,1:19:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 租约是用... - 连活秘书服务公司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- And the lease would be under-- - Greenwood Secretarial Services.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.08,1:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阁下是... - 连桃丽...我喜欢你的套装\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- And you are... - Doris Greenwood. l like your suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.62,1:20:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你 - 明天会有个影印机送来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Well, thank you. - A copier's being delivered tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.56,1:20:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会确保办公室开着 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'll make sure the office is open. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.96,1:20:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我会行使确实 而尊荣的途径”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''l will employ such means only as are consistent with truth and honour.''
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.97,1:20:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我会行使确实 而尊荣的途径”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''l will employ such means only as are consistent with truth and honour.''
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.87,1:20:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我会保障我当事人的 私隐权”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''l will preserve inviolate the secrets of my client.''
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.48,1:20:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我会保障我当事人的 私隐权”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''l will preserve inviolate the secrets of my client. ''
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.19,1:20:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我会以坦诚的态度 执行我的专业”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''l will honestly conduct myself in the practice of my profession'' -
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.32,1:20:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“达致我最好的技术和能力 求主保佑”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- ''to the best of my skill and ability, so help me God.''
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.21,1:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我会保障我当事人的私隐”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}''l will preserve inviolate the secrets of my client.''
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.32,1:21:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要做的第一件事 就是侵犯我当事人的私隐权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}First thing l'm gonna do is violate the secrets of my clients.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.02,1:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看还有别的方法吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Do you see any other way?.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.26,1:21:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，那么我们尽了力没有？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK, then. Aren't we doing the best we can?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.27,1:21:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.37,1:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.51,1:21:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.22,1:21:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.66,1:21:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.27,1:21:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个晚上... 你打电话到开曼的那一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That night... That night in the Caymans when you telephoned...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.67,1:21:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去了沙滩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You were on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.05,1:22:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.92,1:22:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.43,1:22:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.90,1:22:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.69,1:22:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她是谁？ - 我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Who was she? - l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.99,1:22:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不知道？ - 我根本不知道她的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}-You don't know?l don't even know her name.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.23,1:22:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不是有意的 - 才不是，它是件大事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt didn't mean anything. - Like hell, it didn't. lt means a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.87,1:23:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.84,1:23:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛你离开我一晚 就跟陌生人在沙滩上做爱？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why did you fuck some stranger on a beach one night away from me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.54,1:23:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是谁做的？ - 艾佩，我答应你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Who does that? - Abby, l promise you--
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.35,1:23:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.08,1:23:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不能答应了 以后都不可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You can't promise anything. Not ever. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.82,1:23:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你要告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why did you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.59,1:23:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不能忍受不说出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Because l couldn't stand not to.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.46,1:23:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能忍受你不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l couldn't stand your not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.47,1:23:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Now l know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.07,1:23:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 把锁匙给我  - 对不起，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Give me the keys.Sorry, l . . .
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.45,1:23:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把锁匙给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Just give me the keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.60,1:24:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不是只有两个吉姆兄弟吗？ - 韦利，坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Aren't there just two Brothers Grimm? - Sit down, Avery.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.57,1:24:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼和祖儿下周会来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Anthony and Joey are coming down next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.47,1:24:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 干嘛？ - 你的门生有一个哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What for?. - Your protege's got a brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.98,1:24:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那又如何？ - 他在面试时没有提过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- So... - No mention of him at his interview.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.65,1:24:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我有个哥哥可能也不会提及 - 他的哥哥在狱中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l got a brother l might not speak of-- - His brother's doing time.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.65,1:24:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你怎么知道？ - 你以为我是什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- How do you know that? - What do you think l am?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.19,1:24:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一个他妈的看更吗？ - 有时我混淆了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- A fuckin' night watchman? - l get confused sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.09,1:24:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不要！ - 好了，韦利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Well, don't. - All right, Avery.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.40,1:24:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在阿肯色州有一个狱警 他是帮会里的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We got a prison guard in Arkansas. He's on the arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.40,1:24:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉我们有一个叫麦雷的人 犯了杀人罪，正在服刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He tells us about a Ray McDeere doing time for manslaughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.04,1:24:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从郭文迪和何约瑟之后 莫鲁图家族一直都很紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The Moroltos have been edgy since Kozinski and Hodges.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.24,1:24:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们担心我们看错了麦文俊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They're concerned that we're misreading McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.71,1:24:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫氏家族要来亲自接手？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The Moroltos are coming to personally take over?.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.28,1:24:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们是否看错了他？ - 我认为没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Are we misreading him? - l don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.02,1:24:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有个家人是罪犯 你可会说谎？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Wouldn't you lie if you had a felon in the family?.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.22,1:25:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得 我们应该把他扯紧一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l still think we should keep him on a tight leash.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.02,1:25:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？ 你又没有惹人怀疑的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why?. You've got nothing to be suspicious about.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.26,1:25:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有惹人怀疑的事时 我的职责是怀疑别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l get paid to be suspicious when l got nothing to be suspicious about.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.17,1:26:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦先生，你没有听着 - 抱歉，你在说钟数吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You're not listening, Mr. McDeere. - Sorry. You were talking about hours?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.87,1:27:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我不是你们的大客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know l'm not Bendini Lambert's most valuable client -
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.01,1:27:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我有一个合理的投诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- but l've got a legitimate complaint.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.65,1:27:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在上个月并没有 为我的户口花上三十三个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You never spent 33 hours last month on my account.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.22,1:27:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你被追讨那个数目？ - 你没有看你们的帐单吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- ls that what you were billed? - You don't see your own bills?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.82,1:27:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我只是提交我的时间记录 - 它在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- No, l just submit my timesheet. - Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.66,1:27:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在公司经理的档案里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}On file with the office manager.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.69,1:27:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滥收费用变得很普遍 没有人会理会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You know,this overbilling's gotten so common nobody gives it another thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.54,1:27:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就好像给小费 - 缪先生，这不是公司的政策\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's kind of like tipping. - lt's not policy, Mr. Mulholland.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.11,1:27:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直像政策一样 多年来都是那样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt sure seems like policy. lt's been going on for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.48,1:27:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们还忘记了一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}People forget something else, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.92,1:27:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当那边的人 在这上面贴上邮票寄出去时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}When somebody over there put a stamp on this and mailed it -
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.52,1:27:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可知道会有何后果？ 触犯联邦法例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- you know what happened? lt became a federal offence.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.76,1:27:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're damn right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.63,1:27:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 每次违法会被罚... - 一万元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Each instance punishable by-- - ...a $10,000 fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.93,1:27:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每项要坐监三至四年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Three to five years each instance.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.84,1:28:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（时间收费记录： 麦文俊）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.22,1:28:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 我过去缪浩伦那里半小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Nina, l'm going over to Mulholland's for a half hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.33,1:28:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Alrightie.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.96,1:28:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 等一会 - 我收到传呼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Wait a minute. - l got a beeper.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.30,1:28:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个办法可以避免 被吊销资格和犯法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}There's a way of doing this without getting disbarred or breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.20,1:28:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是否我们的首要事项？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ls that our chief concern here?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.77,1:28:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撕掉那些 我可能不需要用它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Tear those up. l might not have to use 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.14,1:28:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要得到 在开曼的那些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But l gotta get to that stuff in the Caymans.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.08,1:28:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？为了联邦调查局？ - 不，为了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What? For the FBl? - No, for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.48,1:28:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过他们不会放过你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They won't let you go, you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.15,1:28:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要找个人用别的方法拿到它 还要尽快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Somebody's gonna have to get to it another way. lt has to happen fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.69,1:29:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要想办法怎样安置雷 - 为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l gotta figure out what to do about Ray. - Why?.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.40,1:29:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毅迪的东西里 可有一个无线录音装置？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ln Eddie's stuff, is there a wireless recording device?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.67,1:29:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有的 - 你懂得使用它吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Yes. Yes. - Do you know how to use it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.08,1:29:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毅迪说我是最佳拍档\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Whenever Eddie said ''my associate'', yours truly.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.35,1:29:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可有高速摄影机？ - 当然有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Were there any high-speed cameras? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.42,1:29:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你去找一辆小型货车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l want you to get hold of a van, Tammy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.78,1:29:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾维斯有没有发现毅迪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Did Elvis ever find out about Eddie?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.39,1:30:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他爱毅迪，你说笑吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Man, he loved Eddie. You kidding?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.56,1:30:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我十八岁时 我和艾维斯已经没有感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That stuff was over between me and Elvis when l was 18.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.53,1:30:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们结了婚两年 有一天早上他觉得我太老了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We'd been married two years. One morning l turned too old for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.20,1:30:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都爱艾维斯 他是个好人，会为我做任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Everybody loves Elvis. He's a panda. He'd do anything for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.68,1:30:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 狗试过追到那骨头吗？ - 听说间中会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Doesn't a dog ever get the bone? - l hear it happens once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.62,1:30:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个灾难 他们不能令那头狗再出赛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's a disaster. They can never get that dog to run again.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.02,1:30:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡先生叫我告诉你 局方十分感激...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. Voyles wants me to tell you how much the Bureau appreciates--
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.86,1:30:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一百万元... 存入瑞士一个保密户口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}A million dollars... ln a numbered account in Switzerland.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.66,1:30:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在苏黎世的IBG国际银行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lBG Bank, lnternational, in Zurich.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.43,1:30:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你一夜间变得贪婪起来 - 还要立即释放我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You sure turned greedy over night. - And my brother out. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.91,1:30:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你哥哥是个被定罪的犯人 - 那么你去找别人做卧底好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Your brother's a convicted felon. - Then get yourself another snitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.94,1:30:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他因杀人入狱的 - 那是在酒吧打架\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- He's in for manslaughter. - lt was a brawl in a bar.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.48,1:31:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他没有玩过拳击 就只会是自卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf he hadn't done any boxing, it would have been self-defence.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.92,1:31:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那仍然是一项罪行 - 你听到了，立即释放我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's still a felony. - You heard me. My brother out now.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.92,1:31:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要加至一百五十万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And make it a million and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.95,1:31:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如你跪地求饶 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How about you get down on your knees and kiss my ass 
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.46,1:31:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别要我控告你做同谋吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}for not indicting you as a co-conspirator right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.33,1:31:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你这个哈佛混蛋！ - 你知道我什么也没做过！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- you Harvard cocksucker! - You know l haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.83,1:31:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会理会？我是联邦密探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Who gives a fuck?. l'm a federal agent -
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.97,1:31:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你这个下流混蛋！ - 你的生命是属于我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- you lowlife motherfucker. Your life is mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.47,1:31:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用侵犯你的公民权利 也可以踢掉你的牙齿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can kick your teeth out your asshole without violating your civil rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.14,1:31:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是戴韦恩探员 - 不错，就是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You are Agent Wayne Tarrance. - You're goddamn right l am.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.29,1:31:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是？ - 你是戴韦恩吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Yeah. - ls this Wayne Tarrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.62,1:31:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是谁？ - 你是戴韦恩吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Who is this? - ls this Wayne Tarrance?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.72,1:31:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的，我是戴韦恩 - 这个也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Yeah, this is Wayne Tarrance. - So is this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.23,1:31:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 混蛋！ - 你知道我什么也没做过！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- ...sucker. - You know l haven't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.76,1:31:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会理会？我是联邦密探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Who gives a fuck? l'm a federal agent-
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.80,1:31:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个下流混蛋！ 你的生命是属于我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- you lowlife motherfucker. Your life is mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.27,1:31:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用侵犯你的公民权利 也可以踢掉你的牙齿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can kick your teeth out your asshole without violating your civil rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.51,1:32:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你该重新考虑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Now, l think you ought to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.47,1:32:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能找到一个脱身的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l think l may have found a way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.48,1:32:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是完全脱身 是一个折冲办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Not out exactly. lt's more like a way through.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.42,1:32:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一个大胆尝试 不过是合法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's a long shot, but it's. . . Well , it's legal.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.83,1:32:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白这样做很怪 但若我们遵守法律就可能得救\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know it's weird, but if we follow the law, it just might save us.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.64,1:33:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不想听一下那个计划 - 它可会改变我们之间的事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}-You don't want to hear the plan. - Does it change anything between us?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.11,1:33:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它只是一个计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's just a plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.92,1:33:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再这样做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.69,1:33:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮不到你，也帮不到我自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can't help you here. l can't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.96,1:33:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经通知了学生 在星期三离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l've given notice at the school. l leave Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.91,1:33:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对，你走了还好 比较安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're right. lt's better if you go. lt's safer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.73,1:33:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不知道 - 不要说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You have no idea. - Don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.47,1:34:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾佩，我爱你 - 你休想，混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l love you, Abby. - Don't you dare, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.75,1:34:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要把计划告诉我吗？ - 明天吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You want to tell me your plan? - Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.52,1:34:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩，你会去哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Abby, where you gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.09,1:34:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先去我父母的家 之后就不知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}To my parents first. After that, l don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.97,1:34:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样离去可能不安全 除非他们知道原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt might not be safe for you to leave, unless they know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.91,1:34:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.34,1:34:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道...在里面某处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know... somewhere... inside...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.45,1:34:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中...公司在听着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...in the dark... the firm is listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.56,1:35:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们进去作个记录吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Should we go in now and do this for the record?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.12,1:35:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下了决定，妈妈身体不好 她要做一些检查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l've made a decision. My mother hasn't been weIl,she's having some tests.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.12,1:35:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去陪她 我们反正也不常见面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l want to be there. We never see each other anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.68,1:35:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也需要一点时间去考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And l need some time to think.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.46,1:35:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找戴比尧，她要离开他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Call Devasher. She's leaving him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.67,1:35:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敲...心情不好吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Knock, knock. Bad times, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.64,1:35:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佩打了电话给琪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Abby called Kay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.75,1:36:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有老婆在第一年 都会有点神经质的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Listen, all the wives go a little nuts the first year.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.75,1:36:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会回来的，可能想要孩子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}She'll be back. Probably want to get pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.36,1:36:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮倒忙，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Big help, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.93,1:36:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个小子是否要教我们 如何管理国内的刑罚制度？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ls this kid gonna tell us how to run the penal system in this country?.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.57,1:36:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他这样才肯交出那些档案 - 那么拖延那笔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's the only way he'll give us the files. - Then stall on the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.64,1:36:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以联邦传召方式释放那个哥哥 跟踪着他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Get the brother out with the federal subpoena. Follow him -
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.94,1:36:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一得到那些档案 就抓他回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and the minute we get the files, yank him back.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.32,1:36:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 颜氏潜水公司 - 麻烦你颜道文先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Abanks Dive Lodge. - Mr. Thomas Abanks, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.92,1:36:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是麦文俊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This is Mitch McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.48,1:37:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我要在早餐会议前 查证一个客户的帐单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Sorry. l gotta justify a client's bill before a breaKfast meeting -
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.15,1:37:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的时间记录和帐单 都锁起了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and all the timesheets and bills are locked up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.18,1:37:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不知道可否这样做 - 你想吵醒韦利吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l don't know if l should do this. - Hey, you wanna wake up Avery?.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.48,1:37:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想打掉一宗对我们的诉讼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm just trying to head off a legal action against us.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.19,1:37:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答应在办公时间前 把所有东西放回原位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l promise. l'll have everything back in the drawer before the office opens.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.44,1:37:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（骆礼顿总时间： 43.3）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.41,1:37:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（总时间： 49.2）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.28,1:37:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（马洛斯总时间： 26.8）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.05,1:37:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（总时间： 30.2）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.41,1:37:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（林利华总时间： 23.8）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.18,1:37:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（总时间： 26.1）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.69,1:37:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你比我想像还要高 - 听来很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You're taller than l thought. - That's nice to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.77,1:38:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划有变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}There's been a change of plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.07,1:38:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不知道有个计划 - 也好，因为已经改变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l didn't know there was a plan. - Good, because it's been changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.14,1:38:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甜心，你是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Who are you, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.75,1:38:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 颜氏潜水公司 - 韦利几时要船？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Abanks Diving Lodge. - What time is Avery taking the boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.49,1:38:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两点半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}2：30.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.66,1:38:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要影印所有的文件 我们要尽量拖延他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We gotta keep him out long enough to copy everything in that closet.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.06,1:38:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心，我的朋友们会带他去 圣三一洞，要六个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Don't worry. My friends are taking him to Trinity Caves. Should be 6 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.96,1:38:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谭美明天会到来准备一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK. Tammy's coming down tomorrow to set things up.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.11,1:38:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以...炒一些蛋吃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can... whip us up some eggs.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.78,1:38:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想最后一天迟到上课\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The last day l don't want to be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.00,1:39:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谭美出发去见颜道文没有？ - 今晚才去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Has Tammy left to meet Abanks? - Not 'til this evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.40,1:39:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在发号施令吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're running a real 3-ring circus, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.31,1:39:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 希望一切顺利 - 一定要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l hope it goes well. - lt has to.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.52,1:39:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否很有趣？ 你去偷情，我却感到内咎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lsn't it amazing? You did the cheating and l feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.62,1:39:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.10,1:39:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.14,1:39:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看招！ - 别那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- There! - Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.08,1:39:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手套在哪里？ 去玩球吧，舒娜，你也去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Where are your gloves? Get back in the dodgeball game. You too, Sheila.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.56,1:40:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男孩和女孩，为未来作彩排吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Boys and girls together, rehearsing for later life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.76,1:40:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在这里干嘛？ - 你可会相信我在附近？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What are you doing here? - Can you believe l was in the area?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.97,1:40:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.34,1:40:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说今天是你最后的一天 真的吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l heard this was your last day. Was l misinformed?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.28,1:40:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会离开一会儿 - 我顺便过来道别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'll be gone for a while. - l just stopped off to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.68,1:40:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 万一... - 万一什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Just in case. - ln case what?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.02,1:40:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一不是一会儿 明天我要去开曼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ln case it's more than a while. l'm going to the Caymans tomorrow -
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.52,1:40:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会错过道别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and l would miss saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.36,1:40:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你，一路顺风 - 要来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Thank you. Have a nice trip. - Wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.67,1:40:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道听来很荒谬 不妨考虑一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know. l know. lt sounds outrageous, but think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.41,1:40:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以晒太阳、潜水 喝夏湾拿酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We could grab some sun, take a dip. Drink some Havana Club.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.28,1:41:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以给你婚姻指导和追求你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l could give you marital advice and hit on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.49,1:41:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样 我答应对拒绝处之泰然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And whatever happens... l promise. l take rejection well.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.86,1:41:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么以为我需要婚姻指导？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What makes you think l need marital advice?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.22,1:41:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，你给我婚姻指导好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Okay, you give me marital advice.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.23,1:41:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l couldn't possibly.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.47,1:41:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不懂潜水 - 很好，我也不懂潜水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l don't scuba dive. - Perfect. l can't scuba dive either.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.54,1:41:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Really?.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.17,1:41:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听说你不会错过机会的 - 这次不行，我要缩短行程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'd heard that you don't miss a chance. - Not this time. l had to shorten the trip.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.95,1:41:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有客户要来，我不能 在二十四小时内潜水和飞行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}A client's coming into town. l can't dive and fly in the same 24 hours. You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.29,1:41:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么样？ - 我母亲病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- How about it? - My mother isn't well.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.19,1:41:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做一些检查 所以我要回家去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They're doing some tests. That's why l'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.76,1:41:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉，我不知道 - 你又怎会知道？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l'm sorry. l didn't know. - How could you possibly.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.24,1:42:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望她早日康复 如果她没事，带她一起来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hope she feels better. And if she does, bring her with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.48,1:42:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，韦利，一路顺风\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Goodbye, Avery. Have a good flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.64,1:42:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 连活秘书服务公司 - 谭美，我是麦艾佩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Greenwood Secretarial Services.Tammy, this is Abby McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.66,1:42:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有麻烦了 韦利不会去潜水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l think you've got a serious problem. Avery isn't going diving.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.63,1:42:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We're dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.11,1:42:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎...？我怎告诉文俊？ 怎让他知道？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How do we...? How do l tell Mitch? How do l let him know?.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.32,1:42:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我反正会去，我要想办法 我三小时后起飞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm going anyway. l gotta try to do something. My flight's in 3 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.67,1:43:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦先生办公室，他不在 要留言吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. McDeere's office. He's not in. May l take a message?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.69,1:43:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谭美什么都别告诉文俊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Tammy, don't tell Mitch anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.63,1:43:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll just be a sec.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.13,1:43:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦艾佩的药方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Prescription for Abigail McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.05,1:43:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}One.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.79,1:43:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想走还是想留下来？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Do you wanna go or do you wanna stay here?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.96,1:43:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不替他扣上手铐？ - 我会做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Aren't you gonna cuff him? - l'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.89,1:44:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是？ - 猜我在看什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Yeah?Guess what I'm looking at?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.68,1:44:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 告诉我 - 六年来第一次的日落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Tell me. - My first sunset in six years.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.35,1:44:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你成功了 - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You made it. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.36,1:44:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，小兄弟，我欠了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Yeah, l did. l owe you, little brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.26,1:44:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.47,1:44:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有颜道文的消息吗？ - 听说一切都准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Anything from Abanks? - Last l heard, everything was set.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.04,1:44:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.01,1:44:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt already is.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.08,1:44:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷，再见吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Be seeing you, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.82,1:44:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，你跟他谈过了 档案在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK, you spoke to him. Where are the files?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.58,1:44:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 钱在哪里？ - 我拿到档案才给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Where's the money?. - Not until l get the files.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.55,1:45:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在汇一半来 户口号码是6194408S\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You send half now. Account number 6194408S.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.69,1:45:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听到吗？ - 听到，6194408S\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You got that? - Yeah, 6194408S.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.90,1:45:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我证实收到钱后 就会寄档案给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}When l get confirmation it's there, l'll send the files.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.98,1:45:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一些零用钱 阿麦，你自由了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Here's some pocket money. You're free, McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.45,1:45:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四分一哩外有一个巴士站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}There's a busstop 1/4 mile.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.22,1:45:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沿着黄线走，你以前也习惯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Follow the yellow line. You're used to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.03,1:46:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.55,1:46:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看来不很惊奇 - 我十分惊奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You don't seem that surprised. - l'm deeply surprised.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.83,1:46:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So am l.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.44,1:47:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 两杯夏湾拿酒 - 好的，杜先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Two Havana Clubs, please? - Yes, Mr. Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.69,1:47:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 验身检查怎样？ - 我们是虚惊一场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- How'd the test turn out? - We were worried for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.80,1:47:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.27,1:47:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又觉得我们在校园时不太融洽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l didn't think we got on that well in the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.37,1:47:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 也许由那时起我长大了 - 那最好不过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Maybe l've grown up since then. - l'd love to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.20,1:47:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很好味 - 是吗？它很像干邑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's delicious. - lsn't it? lt's like cognac.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.34,1:48:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名声十分差\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You know l have a very bad reputation.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.48,1:48:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎会的？ - 我到处留情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What do you do? - l run around.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.05,1:48:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.95,1:48:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为我太太了解我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l think it's because my wife understands me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.82,1:48:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我很爱我的太太\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The fact is l love my wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.13,1:48:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她...对我失去了兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And she's-- She's lost interest in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.67,1:48:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know l have.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.91,1:48:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我自此没有喜欢过别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But l haven't cared for anyone since.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.28,1:48:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'd like to, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.41,1:48:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怀念那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l miss it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.52,1:49:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对首次约会的女孩很坦白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You lay a lot on a girl for a first date.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.33,1:49:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一次约会？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ls that what this is?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.44,1:49:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是B组，我们会驰进五号站 停留二十分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This is Unit B. We'll be pulling into Five Points for a 20 minute rest stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.98,1:49:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苏达龙先生，抱歉这样晚找你 我想跟你谈一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mrs. Sutherland, sorry to call so late, but l need to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.49,1:49:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我先告诉你 你不是我们唯一要找的客户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Let me preface this. You're not the only client l've had to call about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.13,1:50:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要一大片半生熟牛排 三只煎蛋，薯条和咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'd like a big steak medium rare, three fried eggs over, french fries and coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.24,1:50:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（弗利鲶鱼场 阿肯色州卡殊镇）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.71,1:50:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见吧，亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll see you, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.63,1:51:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（收件）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.53,1:51:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（麦雷在联邦传召法例下 已离去）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.41,1:51:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（没有上手铐、没有目的地 没有归期）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.78,1:52:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Aw, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.13,1:52:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么事？ 我们失掉你哥哥的踪影\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What the hell is going on? We lost your brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.73,1:52:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为什么？你们在跟踪他？ - 你想耍我吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Why?. Were you following him? - Are you trying to fuck with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.00,1:52:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在哪里？档案在哪里？ - 你想耍我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Where are you? Where are the files? - You trying to fuck with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.21,1:52:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要档案吗？先汇钱 - 我要马上拿到档案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Want the files? You wire the money. - l want those files now.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.74,1:52:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要挂线了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Gotta go, Wayne.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.08,1:52:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他清楚知道他哥哥在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He knows exactly where his brother is.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.88,1:52:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查一下十一时四十五分 在那餐馆用信用卡入油的记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Check all the credit cards used for fuel at that diner between 1 1 ：00 and 1 1 ：45.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.29,1:52:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们失掉雷的时间 不会多过十一、二个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Whenever we lost Ray... Couldn't be more than a dozen.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.93,1:52:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是其中一个，拿一张 路易斯安那州的地图给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's got to be on one of them. And get me a map of Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.87,1:53:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿一张 路易斯安那州的地图给我！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Get me a map of Louisiana !
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.11,1:53:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水还没有溶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt hasn't even begun to melt.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.44,1:53:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,员工最懂得掌握时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The staff was chosen for its timing.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.03,1:54:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会自己来，但总做不成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l would do that, but l could never do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.67,1:54:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些钮扣太小了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The buttons are too small.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.54,1:54:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 要身手灵光 - 是灵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt requires terrible ''desktermindy''. - ''Dexterity''.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.71,1:54:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真神奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.12,1:55:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你来这里干嘛？ - 什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What are you doing here? - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.39,1:55:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你到底为什么来这里？ - 我以为我被邀请的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Exactly what did you come here for?. - l thought l was invited.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.20,1:55:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不诚实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're not being truthful.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.24,1:55:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为何你这样做？ - 因为我不舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Why are you doing this? - Because l'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.28,1:55:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你把实情告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l want you to tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.65,1:55:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这里为了惩罚文俊 让公司支配我们的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l came here to punish Mitch for letting the firm run our lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.02,1:55:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来是因为文俊跟你来这里时 他跟别人上床\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l came because when Mitch was here with you, he slept with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.82,1:55:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否想听这些？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ls that what you want to hear?.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.53,1:55:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这比别个版本好一点 - 什么别个版本？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's better than the alternative. - What alternative?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.44,1:55:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来为了想见我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That you came here to see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.87,1:56:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦利？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Avery?.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:57.40,1:57:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 三个小时前收到的 - 你肯定他没事吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt came in about three hours ago. - Are you sure l'll be all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.24,1:57:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎样做？报警？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What the hell you wanna do? Call 9 1 1?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.74,1:57:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿那条锁匙、抓着东西 就过来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Get the key, grab the stuff, and get over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.41,1:57:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续找他，叫醒那个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Keep calling him. Wake the son of a bitch up.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.12,1:57:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在电话找到他就叫我 我要那个女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}When you get him on the phone, find me. l want that girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.93,1:57:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,户口号码是6194408S\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Account number 6194408S.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.87,1:57:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是七十五万吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And can you confirm that it's $750,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.86,1:57:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，我现在准备离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Absolutely. l'm fixin' to get out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:52.86,1:57:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你拿到我要的所有资料吗？ - 拿到了，但文俊...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You got all the information l need? - Yeah, but Mitch...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.80,1:58:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看过那些东西 但是没有列出数字的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...l've been looking at the stuff and there's no numbers listed.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.94,1:58:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没有数字？没有银码？ - 没有，有些银行户口的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- There's no numbers? No amounts? - No, l got papers from bank accounts -
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.94,1:58:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从开曼到香港都有 却没有银码\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- everywhere from the Caymans to Hong Kong, but there's no amounts.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.24,1:58:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我耍不出什么招数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l can't play the poker game l'm gonna play and bluff.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.45,1:58:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们有多少钱和在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How much do they have and where?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:16.98,1:58:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每项上面都写着：\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}There's a note on each one that says...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.72,1:58:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“资料在客户里和我的电脑” 签名A.T\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...''lnfo held by client and my Mac.'' Signed ''A.T.''
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.22,1:58:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的资料吗？有密码吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ls there any other information? ls there a password?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.49,1:58:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谭美，看一看那份文件 - 等一会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Just look on the paper, Tammy. - Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.47,1:58:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,括号里写着...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ln parentheses it says...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.74,1:58:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R- E- F，然后冒号 然后 “歌莉亚”\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...R-E-F, then a colon, then ''Cordelia''.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.61,1:58:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 在早上我要查韦利的电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK. l gotta get to Avery's computer in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.08,1:58:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点，我们不知道 早上的情况会怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Be careful. We don't know how all this will look in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.98,1:58:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会顺利度过早上的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll get through the morning fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.32,1:58:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们发觉我午饭后没有回来 我已经在芝加哥了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}When they notice l'm not back from lunch, l'll be in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.63,1:59:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大功告成，我要拿这些到船上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK, we're done. l gotta get these on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.50,1:59:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船？什么船？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The boat? What boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:07.03,1:59:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该把文俊进行着的事告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Man, there's some stuff l gotta tell you about what Mitch is doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.81,1:59:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说吧，什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Tell me. What?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:13.27,1:59:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把锁匙拿回去 在他醒来前快离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Get the keys back and get out before he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:36.06,1:59:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.10,1:59:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要再说一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You have to repeat that.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:48.54,1:59:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不可能的 - 她们偷了你的锁匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- That's not possible. - They've stolen your keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.65,1:59:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她究竟是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Now, who the hell is she?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.95,2:00:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你了解我吧，我昨晚认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You know me. Somebody l met last night.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.09,2:00:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她又怎会知道要拿你的锁匙？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How the hell does she know to go after your keys?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.16,2:00:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙在十分钟内降落了 她最好在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The guys are landing in 10 minutes. She'd better be there.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.39,2:00:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.96,2:00:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在电话中听到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They heard you on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.70,2:00:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊叫你来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mitch sent you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:57.14,2:01:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我知他是个空谈理想主义者 - 他不知道我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l knew he was a closet idealist. - He doesn't know l'm here.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:03.65,2:01:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我是为了他做的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But l did do it for him.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.49,2:01:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那比跟他拉平还好一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's even better than getting even with him.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.39,2:01:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You gotta get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:21.27,2:01:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你打算怎样做？ - 艾佩，那个女孩是个布局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What are you gonna do? - Abby, the girl was a set-up.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.61,2:01:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在沙滩上...她是个布局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}On the beach, she was a set-up.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.31,2:01:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们做那种事的 万一惯常的引诱行不通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They do things like that. Just in case the usual inducements don't work.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.85,2:01:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会怎样对付你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What are they gonna do to you?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.86,2:01:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样也好... 他们很久以前已经做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Whatever it is... they did it a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:52.50,2:01:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 搬走这东西 - 不是你的棉花货车或你的巷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Get this thing out of here. - lt ain't your cotton truck or your alley.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.04,2:01:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你别吵 - 我现在就找交通部\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Just cool it. - l'm calling the traffic department now.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.44,2:02:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他有电话来吗？ - 还没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Did he call? - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.35,2:02:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚跟华利说过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l just spoke to Avery.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.45,2:02:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要在十点前做好一些工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He needs some work done before 10：00.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.58,2:02:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在他的电脑做吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll just get it off his computer.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:16.76,2:02:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这班人怎么了？ 这东西的纸用光了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What the hell's the matter with you guys? This thing's out of paper.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.20,2:02:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（传送银行）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.21,2:02:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（联合户口记录）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.78,2:02:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦文俊回来了没有？ 搜查每一层，他做了一项交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ls McDeere in yet? Check every goddamn floor. He cut a deal.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.96,2:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 雷迪新、欧礼宏、何谭美... - 何谭美？那是卢毅迪的秘书\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Natisin, Earlywine, Hemphill... - Hemphill? That's Lomax's secretary.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:00.20,2:03:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是威斯维监狱的杜力海狱长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's Warden Dynehart from Wrightsville Prison.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.80,2:03:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有麻烦了，我刚盘问一个狱警 她擅自发了一份传真\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We got a problem. l just questioned a guard who sent an unauthorized fax -
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.47,2:03:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到一间在孟菲斯的律师行 是关于你们的囚犯的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- to a Memphis law firm. lt was in regard to your prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.68,2:03:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:23.46,2:03:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人，他不在他的办公室 我查一下他是否在大厦里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's not in his office, your Honour. l'll see if he's in the building.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:31.23,2:03:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢你，美芝 - 不用客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Thank you, Madge. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.90,2:03:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊，我们到处找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mitch? We've just been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.24,2:03:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麻烦你进来 - 杜先生办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Can you step in here, please? - Mr. Tolar's office.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.28,2:03:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，他在这里，接线吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's right here, Nina. Transfer him.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:47.65,2:03:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦先生？戴韦恩法官找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. McDeere? Judge Tarrance for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.09,2:03:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.80,2:04:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂？ - 快走！ 他们知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Hello. - Get out of there! They know.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.27,2:04:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到吗？快走，立刻来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hear what l said? Get out of there. Get over here now.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:21.30,2:04:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你可以走吗？ - 我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Can you? l understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:36.10,2:04:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卢迪，他逃不到哪里 到前门去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's going nowhere. Rudy, get to the front door.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.41,2:04:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊！ 有什么可以效劳？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mitch! What can l do you for?.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:54.98,2:04:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.93,2:05:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卢迪，他向东面走进巷里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK, Rudy. He's headed east up the alley.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.67,2:05:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓着他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Get him and hold him.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.34,2:05:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死，我早知道他们找不到她 叫他坐那班机回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Goddamnit, l knew they wouldn't find her. Get him back on that plane.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.55,2:05:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在麦文俊 去找联邦调查局前抓不到他...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf we don't get McDeere before he gets to the Feds...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.92,2:05:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他走向哪一方？ - 是麦文俊！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- What direction was he running? - lt's McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.56,2:05:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在哪里？ - 别管了，发生了什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Where are you? - Never mind. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.93,2:05:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，我叫一辆车来接你 快来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's OK. l'll send you a car. Just come on in.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.76,2:05:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你来到后我再告诉你 - 不，你现在告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'll tell you when you get here.You just come on in.No, you tell me now!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.10,2:05:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一个狱警，快来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt was a prison guard. Just come on in.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.27,2:05:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会给你人身监护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We'll place you in protective custody.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.51,2:05:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你没有令我感到受保护 - 你想被杀死吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You don't make me feel protected. - Are you looking to get whacked?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.68,2:05:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可知道发生什么事？ 莫鲁图家族今天抵达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Do you know what's going on? The Moroltos arrive today.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.68,2:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 从芝加哥来了 - 什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- From Chicago. - What?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.31,2:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我面前有他们的行程表 莫氏家族要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l got their itinerary right in front of me. The Moroltos are coming here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.65,2:06:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟菲斯...这个下午 行程表就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Memphis. This afternoon. The itinerary's right here.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.52,2:06:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西北航空，两点十六分抵达 直去皮布迪酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Northwest, arrives 2: 16pm. Straight to the Peabody.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.49,2:06:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界都在找你，你不能回家 所以马上来这里吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The whole world's looking for you. You can't go home, so get in here now.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.14,2:06:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要失踪数小时，我有事要办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l gotta get lost for a few hours. Something l gotta do.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.91,2:06:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那些档案在哪里？ - 你会跟着收到指示的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Where the hell are the files, Mitch? - You'll get instructions... after.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.41,2:06:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}After what?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.72,2:06:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在扣留证据 他拿了我们七十五万元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's withholding evidence. He's got 3/4 of a million dollars of our money.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.32,2:06:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个逃犯，我要抓他回来 用孟菲斯警方去抓他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's a fugitive. l want him brought in. Use the Memphis police, but get him.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:49.99,2:06:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一辆红色十吨货车 由一间弗利鲶鱼场登记的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's a red KW 1 0-ton registered to a Farley's Catfish Farm.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.37,2:07:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查它的路线，找那辆货车 发出对麦氏兄弟的详情通报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Get its routes and find that truck. lssue APB's on both McDeere brothers.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.76,2:07:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在1870年间的蒸汽船高峰时期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}During the height of the steamboat era in the 1870s -
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.70,2:07:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有数以百计 像罗拔利号的海上皇宫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- these great floating palaces like the Robert E. Lee numbered by the 100s -
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.54,2:07:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在密西西比河上往来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- on the Mississippi River.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.25,2:07:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请跟我到主甲板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Follow me now to the main deck of the boat...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.52,2:07:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Hey, Mitch. Mitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.88,2:08:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们想我带他们出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...'cause the kids wanted me to bring them by.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.22,2:08:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？什么事？好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why?. What's the matter?. OK.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.49,2:08:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力万？我刚在泥岛博物馆 看见文俊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Oh, Lamar?. l just saw Mitch at Mud lsland Museum.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.26,2:08:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他像个游客般走过 我挥手但他看不到我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He zipped through like a tourist. l waved, but he didn't see me.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.03,2:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（弗利鲶鱼场）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:09:01.80,2:09:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西北航空，第264号班机 从芝加哥抵达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Northwest Airlines, Flight 264, arriving from Chicago...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.28,2:09:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 戴比尧 - 他们在泥岛见到麦文俊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Devasher. - They spotted McDeere on Mud lsland.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.24,2:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上叫人去那里，我跟着就来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Get the boys over there right away. l'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.68,2:09:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这些跟其余的一起放好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK. Let's get these below with the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:31.39,2:09:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 颜氏潜水公司 - 我的朋友们怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Abanks Diving Lodge. - How are my friends?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.03,2:09:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.23,2:09:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥在机上，谭美正在上货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Your brother's on the plane and Tammy's loading the shipment.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:44.34,2:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一切顺利 - 你的律师朋友死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt worked out. - Your lawyer friend is dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.91,2:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有上船，他取消了包船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He never was on the boat. He cancelled the charter.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.32,2:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他怎会... - 他遇溺了...在浴缸里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- How did he-- - He drowned... in his bathtub...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.12,2:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那个女士走了之后 谭美没有告诉你吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}...after the lady left. Didn't Tammy tell you?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.19,2:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？什么女士？ 你怎么知道...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What? What lady?. How did you get the--
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.96,2:10:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，谭美的女朋友 给他下了迷药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't know. Tammy's lady friend slipped him a ''mickey finn''.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.47,2:10:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看是一个他认识的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l think it was somebody he knew.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:16.53,2:10:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？什么女朋友？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What are you talking about? What lady friend?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.21,2:10:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一会...文俊在问起你的 朋友艾佩，那是她的名字吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Wait a minute. Mitch is asking about your friend Abby. lsn't that her name?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.77,2:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:00.96,2:14:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那第一道门吗？ 我从前面走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Come here. See that first door?. l'm going around the front.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:54.47,2:16:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You sick son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,2:17:27.10,2:17:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（皮布迪酒店）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:17:28.73,2:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然可以谈 我不是在谈着吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Of course, l can talk. lsn't that what l'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:31.57,2:17:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫利，如果有别的原因 就告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lf it's something else, please advise me, Maury.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:33.77,2:17:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一向都喜欢 付每小时五百元来学习\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l always like to learn something at $500 an hour.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:36.91,2:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓每个律师都该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l swear, every fucking lawyer should be killed.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.01,2:17:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想什么？你想见麦文俊？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You wanna what? You want to meet with McDeere?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:44.15,2:17:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？ 让你可收我一小时一千元吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}For what? So you can charge me $1 ,000 an hour -
Dialogue: 0,2:17:47.72,2:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你就把我关进监狱 坐三十年？你留在芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- while you send me to Joliet for 30 years? Stay in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:51.26,2:17:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个小时做成了一宗交易 我肯定它是好东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This kid's cut a deal and l bet it's a beaut.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:53.89,2:17:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 如我抓到这个他妈的小子... - 对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lf l get my hands on this fucking kid... - Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:57.60,2:18:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 现在不行 - 莫先生，我想这是急事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Not now. - l think it's urgent, Mr. Morolto.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:01.17,2:18:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 露菲说是急事，你怎么... - 是麦先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Ruthie says it's urgent. What do you... - lt's Mr. McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:05.57,2:18:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦文俊先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mr. Mitchell McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:08.67,2:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在等着见你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He's waiting to see you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:12.41,2:18:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l think Ruth is right.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.27,2:18:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是麦文俊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mitch McDeere.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:42.51,2:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的律师，其中一个吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm your attorney. One of them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.28,2:18:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你已经知道 但我还是说一下，以妨...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l assume you knew, but l thought l'd mention it in case...
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.69,2:18:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 请坐 - 不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Would you care to sit down? - Not really.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:59.29,2:19:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l want to try...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:06.53,2:19:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事...真棘手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}This is just... This is very awkward.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:12.87,2:19:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的律师行 作了一个违反操守的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm afraid my firm has behaved in an unethical manner.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:21.71,2:19:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们...彭林骆律师行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt seems that we - Bendini, Lambert & Locke -
Dialogue: 0,2:19:24.68,2:19:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整间律师行一直进行着...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- the entire firm has been engaged in a -
Dialogue: 0,2:19:28.62,2:19:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一项阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- well, a conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:32.86,2:19:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直...滥收费用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We've been... overbilling our clients.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:54.55,2:19:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一些更是庞大的滥收数目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ln some cases, massive overbilling.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.75,2:20:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我加入这间公司时 我是完全不知情的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l assure you, l had no idea this was going on when l joined the firm.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.96,2:20:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我要举报这种犯罪行为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l feel l have to report this criminal behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:08.69,2:20:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能在没有你们的授权下 使用你们的发票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But l can't use your invoices without your written authorization.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.53,2:20:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们的发票？ - 东尼，听他说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Our invoices? - Tony, please. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.04,2:20:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，你们的帐单是我们 对付滥收费用的重要证据\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Yes, sir. Your bills are an important part of the proof that we've overbilled you.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.95,2:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's it?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.25,2:20:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是了 大部分的客户已经同意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Pretty much. Most of our clients have already agreed.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.32,2:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是全部人，除了你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Pretty much all. Except for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:38.06,2:20:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Which is why l'm here.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:41.23,2:20:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你跟联邦调查局 谈过的事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And this is what you've been talking to the FBl about?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.33,2:20:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你想我们让你把我们的帐单 - 我们收你们的费用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You want us to let you turn our bills-- - What we charged you.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.00,2:20:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 应该说是“超收” 你们 - 交给政府？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l should say ''overcharged'' you... - ...over to the government.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:54.77,2:20:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是的 - 这情况下...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Yes, sir. - ls that in any way--
Dialogue: 0,2:20:57.18,2:21:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会，这样不会影响你在其他 律师与当事人关系范畴上的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}No, sir. lt does not in any way waive your rights to full confidentiality -
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.55,2:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有保密权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- in any other area of the attorney-client relationship.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:08.62,2:21:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你们的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm your lawyer, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:12.12,2:21:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论我喜欢与否 我也不能向政府谈论你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Whether l like it or not, l can't talk to the government about you -
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.03,2:21:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我不再做你们的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- even when l'm no longer your lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.27,2:21:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会违反我作了的誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That would be breaking my word. My oath.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:22.67,2:21:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，文俊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}All right, Mitch.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:25.57,2:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷取档案的事又怎样？ 究竟是什么一回事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What was this stealing of the files? What the fuck was this all about?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.74,2:21:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些档案没有被偷去 它们还是完封不动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The files haven't been stolen. They are in exactly the same place.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:36.88,2:21:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有需要详细了解 你的资产和活动的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt was important for me to be thoroughly familiar with the precise make-up -
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.35,2:21:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际组合和分布地点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- and whereabouts of all the holdings and activities.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:46.93,2:21:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把全部文件都影印了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So, l prepared copies of everything.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.10,2:21:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样你和我就可以沟通得更好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That way you and l can communicate perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:55.73,2:22:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，如果我们需要 跟第三者谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Of course, if we ever have to talk to a third party -
Dialogue: 0,2:22:00.77,2:22:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就清楚知道 每仙、镑、法O和马克的数目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- then l know everything down to the penny, pound, franc and Deutschmark.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:08.68,2:22:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的我都知道 身为你的律师，这是应该的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l know everything you know. As l should. As your attorney.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:16.12,2:22:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果律师行 决定终止雇用你又怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What if the firm should desire to terminate your employment?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:22.13,2:22:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论我知道什么、去到哪里 我都受制于律师与当事人权利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Whatever l know, wherever l go, l am bound by the attorney-client privilege.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:29.74,2:22:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就好像...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l am very much like...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:33.61,2:22:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像一条载着货物 永远泊不到港口的船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l am exactly like a ship carrying a cargo that will never reach any port.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:43.15,2:22:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有生一日 那条船永远都泊不到岸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}As long as l'm alive, the ship will always be at sea.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:49.72,2:22:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像阿拉发是吗？ 每晚都在不同的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Yasser-fucking Arafat, huh? Never a night in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.06,2:23:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何，我需要你的 书面授权，让我可以交出帐单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}ln any case, l need your written authorization so l can release your bills.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:02.50,2:23:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像其他当事人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Like every other client has given.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.68,2:23:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你可有带授权书来？ - 有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You have this authorization with you? - l do.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:31.60,2:23:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（致联邦调查局 戴韦恩探员，麦文俊先生上）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,2:23:37.14,2:23:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 里面有发现吗？ - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Anything in there? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.98,2:23:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:44.74,2:23:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有户口号码？ 你知道怎样取得它？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You got the account number?. You know how to access it?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:48.44,2:23:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文俊证实已经收到钱 是七十五万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Mitch has verified that the money's there.$ 7 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:52.44,2:23:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你那翘起的小嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l love your crook ed little mouth.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:03.03,2:24:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这不是我最好的特征 - 是什么呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- lt's not my best feature. - Wow! What is?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:32.96,2:24:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟在哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Where the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.33,2:24:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么？ 你让莫氏家族逍遥法外？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}What is this? You let the Moroltos off the hook?.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:46.00,2:24:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们是我的当事人 - 他们是坏蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- They're my clients. - They're the crooks.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:47.94,2:24:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让黑手党脱身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're letting the Mafia get away.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:50.34,2:24:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也好不了多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You guys are always one villain behind the times.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:52.34,2:24:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只给我一些 虚报帐单的文职人员？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You give me some ''pencil-pushers'' who padded their bill?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:54.45,2:24:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为他们没有开枪 就不是坏人？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You think if they don't pull guns, they're not the bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:56.92,2:24:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问一问莫氏家族找谁更困难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Ask the Moroltos who's harder to find.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:58.92,2:25:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人凶手还是把他们的钱 收藏起来的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}The killer or the lawyer hiding their money?.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:01.15,2:25:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说废话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Don't give me that shit.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:03.26,2:25:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想抓黑手党吗？ 抓他们的律师吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You want the mafia? Get their lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:05.72,2:25:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有律师行 莫氏家族也洗不到黑钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Without the firm, the Moroltos can only launder money in a washing machine.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.23,2:25:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是天真，外面还有 一千间律师行明天就会洗黑钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You are so naive. There are 1 ,000 other firms who'll launder money tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:14.97,2:25:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你又怎样铲除它们 - 逐间来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- How the hell you gonna get all them? - One at a time.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:19.17,2:25:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个律师，有我的一间 你是个探员，你去抓其余的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l'm a lawyer and l got mine. You're a cop. You get the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:22.98,2:25:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用什么来抓？滥收费用？ 邮件诈骗？真刺激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Get them with what? Overbilling? Mail fraud? That's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:27.05,2:25:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不容易但很有力 罚款一万元和入狱五年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's not sexy, but it's got teeth. $10,000 and five years in prison.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.05,2:25:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是每项罪名十年和五年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's 10 and 5 for each act.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:35.72,2:25:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可有认真看过？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Have you really looked at that?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.22,2:25:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,律师行每个合伙人都虚报帐目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You got every partner in the firm on overbilling.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:41.13,2:25:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有二百五十项文件和邮件诈骗 那是敲诈勒索\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}There's 250 acts of document and mail fraud there. That's racketeering.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:45.06,2:25:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少入狱一千二百五十年 和罚款二百五十万元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}That's minimum 1 ,250 years in prison and $2 1/2 million dollars in fines.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:50.60,2:25:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 比你抓到卡邦的还更多 - 你把事件扭曲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- That's more than you had on Capone. - You twist this into whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:54.34,2:25:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你同意交易为了自保 又拿了七十五万元\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You made a deal to save your ass. You got 3/4 of a million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:58.38,2:26:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然是个高明的律师 而且在这件事中脱身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You're still a hotshot lawyer and you're out of this.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:00.98,2:26:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有收下你们分文 这笔钱是给别人的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l didn't keep a nickel of your money. lt was always for somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:04.08,2:26:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我当过彭林骆律师行的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Yeah, l'm still a lawyer with references from Bendini, Lambert & Locke.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:08.22,2:26:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可想你的履历上有那个？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You wanna put that on your resume?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:11.02,2:26:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我日后开动汽车时 不惊慌吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You think l'm ever gonna turn on my car again without sweating.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:14.56,2:26:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你 为什么你那样做？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l don't understand you. What did you do it for?.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:19.26,2:26:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你赢不到什么 - 有的，我赢回了我的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You didn't win a thing. - Oh, yeah, l did. l won my life back.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.80,2:26:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不支配我，他们也不支配我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You don't run me and they don't run me.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:26.04,2:26:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想知道一件怪事吗？ 我重新发现了法律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You wanna know something weird? l discovered the law again.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:29.17,2:26:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的确令我思考它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You actually made me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:31.21,2:26:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我念了三年法律也没那样做过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l managed to get through three years of law school without doing that.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:38.38,2:26:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在赛狗场上的你 我本可以把它公开的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt's you at the dog track. l could've gone public with it.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.29,2:26:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 为何你没有？ - 那是违法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Why didn't you? - lt's against the law.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:51.06,2:26:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}OK.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:55.40,2:26:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎会想到邮件诈骗的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How in the hell did you ever come up with mail fraud?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:00.71,2:27:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是执业考试题目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}lt was on the bar exam.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:04.01,2:27:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们迫我拼命温习\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}They made me study like hell for it.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:43.28,2:27:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Well...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:46.35,2:27:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忙了一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You've had a busy day.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:50.26,2:27:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}So did you.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:54.46,2:27:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你不把你的全盘计划 告诉我？莫氏家族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Why didn't you tell me the truth about your plan? All of it. The Moroltos.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:00.07,2:28:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我知道你会担心 那样会令你留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Because l knew you'd worry. And that might make you stay.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:05.14,2:28:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道你要离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And l knew you needed to leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:17.68,2:28:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把这里搞得不错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l like what you've done to the place.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:21.42,2:28:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我以为你要去找你的爸妈 - 我有去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- l thought you were going to your folks. - l was.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:27.13,2:28:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兜路回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Some detour.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:32.36,2:28:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要去哪里？ - 去找你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Where are you going? - To look for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:40.37,2:28:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得丢下你不顾而去 是不行的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l guess l didn't feel l could leave you without trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.28,2:28:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可想告诉我发生了什么事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}You wanna tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:54.22,2:28:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改天吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Someday.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:57.96,2:29:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该知道韦利是蛮正派的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l think you should know that Avery was pretty decent.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:04.76,2:29:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是正派、腐败、受害 和那么不快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}He was decent and corrupt and ruined and so unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:11.97,2:29:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾佩，听着... - 整件事都可以发生在你身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Listen, Abby. - lt could have happened to you. All of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:15.01,2:29:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你正步向那个境地 - 我有没有失去你？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You were on your way. - Did l lose you?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:24.98,2:29:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看来很累 - 是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- You look tired. - Did l?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.60,2:29:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}l've loved you all my life.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:44.07,2:29:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使在我们认识以前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Even before we met.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:48.67,2:29:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中也不全是因为你 是因为对你的承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Part of it wasn't even you. lt was just the promise of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:53.68,2:29:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但过去的这几天，你信守诺言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}But these last days you kept your promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:05.96,2:30:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎会失去我？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}How could you lose me?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.89,2:30:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 它会推得到吗？ - 捱到去哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Do you think it will make it? - Make it where?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:45.30,2:30:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 波士顿 - 波士顿有什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- Boston. - What's in Boston?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:49.50,2:30:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}We are.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:53.71,2:30:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有小王店\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And the Wong Boys...
Dialogue: 0,2:30:55.77,2:30:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我的孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}And my kids.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:58.54,2:31:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还有一间不知名的小律师行 - 但有很大的潜质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}- And a very small, unknown law firm. - With a lot of potential.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:05.52,2:31:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14\b0}Yeah.
